Enzymes eat away at odor & stain causing bacteria making this a powerful cleaner that is safe for your home. American-Made Pet Cleaner Sourcing ingredients inside the USA means we can ensure the quality our customers have come to expect from our products. This American-made cleaner will blow outsourced products out of the water using natural, trusted ingredients. Nothing Extra Added This natural and plant based cleaning solution is not only an eco-responsible product, but a powerful odor and stain eliminator. The enzymatic formula doesn't mask odors, but in fact, eats away at odor and stain causing bacteria. Non-Toxic & Biologically Degradable This stain and odor remover is non-toxic and biodegradable. The use of enzymes for cleaning actually helps to remediate pollution situations as they degrade. Read more Meet Kyle, the Owner and Founder of Pawstruck Hi, my name is Kyle, and I’m the founder and owner of Pawstruck . When my dog, Tyson, was a puppy, I visited a pet store to buy him some treats and noticed a disturbing trend. Everything had artificial ingredients. The ingredient lists seemed like gibberish due to the complex scientific jargon (ascorbyl palmitate, hydrogenated hydrolysate, glucosamine hydrochloride…huh???). I started searching the internet in the hopes of finding treats, chews, and pet supplies that were healthy, natural, and reasonably priced. What I was looking for just wasn’t available. Through that frustration came my inspiration for creating Pawstruck. Tyson and I now provide dogs all over the USA with high-quality, natural and affordable dog treats, chews and pet supplies! It didn’t take long for fellow pet owners out there to catch on. We are so grateful for those of you—both canines and humans—who supported our philosophies and business. If you haven't already, we hope you'll join the Pawstruck Pack ! - Kyle & Tyson

title: Plantar Fasciitis Posterior Night Splint - Medium
text: From the brand Mars Med Supply Previous page What makes our products unique? All Mars Wellness products come from a focus on the market to ensure that our items solve daily issues and provide a cost effective solution. How did we get our start? Since 2012 Mars Wellness has been a leader in developing and manufacturing top of the line medical supplies and equipment. Recommended by doctors and patients alike, our products help the patients along the road to recovery. Why do we love what we do? Helping our cusomters makes our work that much easier. Premium products Visit the Store Next page Product Description IMPORTANT: For Wide Or Swollen Feet We Recommend That You Purchase a Size Larger To Ensure Optimal Fit MARS Wellness Plantar Fasciitis Night Splint is primarily intended for treating Plantar Fasciitis and Achilles Tendonitis, and may be ideal for other conditions recommended by a physician. The purpose of this lightweight plantar fasciitis night brace is to keep the patient's ankle in a neutral position overnight, passively stretching the calf and plantar fascia during sleep. This gentle stretch helps reduce the muscle contracture, inflammation, and associated pain. The lightweight, low profile shell is sturdy and breathable and has three padded straps with buckles to ensure immobilization. In addition, the padding features a washable Lycra covering that is cool against the skin for maximum comfort. Recommended Best Practices It will be best to start wearing the night splint for a short period of time, perhaps only 1 hour the first night, then extending it gradually each night and week. Most splints are also adjustable, so you can alter the tension to suit. It may be that you need to start with it looser and make it tighter over time. The ideal target will be to wear it overnight or for around 4 to 5 hours at a time. This is the perfect time period for the plantar fascia tissue to extend and begin to heal! Our uniquely designed night splint includes buckles on both sides of the splint eliminating the need to reach over and struggle to buckle the splint. IMPORTANT FITTING INSTRUCTIONS If you find your foot or heel moving around in the splint, tighten each strap until the splint feels snug-this will help keep your foot in place. D onning Tips Place the splint on the floor, Step into the splint with heel as far back as possible Close and adjust the clasps while the splint is on the floor. Clasping and unclasping can take a couple of times of donning the brace to get used to Read more Common Questions/Concerns That are Asked Where Does the Wedge Go? Step 1 Lift up the fabric pad at the toe area of the boot. Step 2 Slide the wedge underneath and affix to the velcro on the wedge to the velcro on the bottom of the boot. Can be moved around to adjust flexion. Numb feeling in my foot? Experiencing a numb feeling in your foot when wearing the brace? Ironically, this is a sign that the product is doing its job. It takes a couple of days for someone who wears a plantar fasciitis night splint to get used to the stretch provided by the splint. Initially the stretch can be uncomfortable and can sometimes cause numbness, but once a customer wears it for a couple of nights they are then able to tolerate the stretch and the numbness goes away. Common Causes of Plantar Fasciitis Plantar fasciitis is caused by straining the ligament that supports your arch. Repeated strain can cause tiny tears in the ligament which can lead to pain and swelling. This is more likely to happen if: Your feet roll inward too much when you walk (excessive pronation ). You have high arches or flat feet. You walk, stand, or run for long periods of time, especially on hard surfaces. You are overweight. You wear shoes that don't fit well or are worn out. You have tight achilles tendons or calf muscles. Read more About Plantar Fasciitis Plantar fasciitis is the most common cause of heel pain. The plantar fascia is the flat band of tissue (ligament) that connects your heel bone to your toes. It supports the arch of your foot. If you strain your plantar fascia, it gets weak, swollen, and irritated (inflamed). Then your heel or the bottom of your foot hurts when you stand or walk. Plantar fasciitis is common in middle-aged people. It also occurs in younger people who are on their feet a lot, like athletes or soldiers. It can happen in one foot or both feet. So how can the splint help my plantar fasciitis? When wearing the splint, the foot is held in a certain position, called “dorsiflexion“. This means that the fascia is stretched, not allowing it to contract and become tighter overnight. The great thing about a night splint, is that the remedy is quite gentle and the fascia will be returned to it’s proper length over a period of time. Once stretched out, the plantar fascia will become less tense and therefore will cause less pain. TRULY UNIVERSAL Now designed with buckles on both sides of the splint, this allows you to wear it on either foot without having to worry about trying to find which side it opens and closes from. The Mars Wellness Promise Here at Mars Wellness we strive for complete satisfaction. If you are not satisfied or have other questions, we encourage you to reach out to us so we can properly help Read more Read more

title: Over Ear Headphone, Wired Premium Stereo Sound Headsets with 50mm Driver, Foldable Comfortable Headphones with Protein Earmuffs and Shareport for Recording Monitoring Podcast PC TV- with Mic (Silver)
text: From the brand Previous page We are a manufacturer with over 15 years of audio production experience. Our over-ear headphones, designed for extra-long listening sessions. We’ve firmly planted the OneOdio flag in the DJ，Monitor, HIFI industry. Besides, we are also creating more unique sound experiences in ANC industry over 30 countries in Europe, North America, Asia, etc. So far, we have a certain international brand influence and reputation around the whole globe. Passion for good sound Professional Studio Headphones Visit the Store DJ & Music Headphones Visit the Store How did we get our start? Music is an essential part of the human experience. We believe in the power of sound. It can completely change the way we perceive a moment, a movie, a concert or a favorite song. Experience audio with unprecedented intensity and emotion. And we also believe high-quality headphones amplify the pleasant, emotional experience of listening to music.Sound comes first.Then OneOdio came into being. Sound is just the beginning. Next page Product Description What makes OneOdio Pro series a good headphone? Sound Studio Pro-30 is a over ear headphone which has bass sound. The 50mm neodymium driver reproduces all your music's dynamics and delivers controlled bass that audiophiles need. It is ideal for mixer panel, turntable, monitoring in recording studios, radio, film production, video, electronic news gathering--and virtually any application where high quality sound is required. text: Product Description SweetLeaf Sweetener (70-Count Packets), 2.5-Ounce Boxes (Pack of 4) Product Description SweetLeaf Sweetener (70-Count Packets), 2.5-Ounce Boxes (Pack of 4)From the brand Why Choose SweetLeaf? SweetLeaf creates the highest quality products using stevia leaf to make choosing a healthy lifestyle the easy choice. Previous page Jim May "The Father Of Stevia" and founder of SweetLeaf and Wisdom Natural Brands Jim knew there had to be a better option than sugar, and he found it with Stevia. The Stevia plant’s natural sweetness had the potential to naturally replace sugar without the calories, glycemic response, and adverse health effects. He began to import healthful herbal teas from the Amazon rainforest, including Stevia, and created great tasting sugar alternatives. SweetLeaf Classics Have you made the switch from sugar to stevia? If you aren’t exactly sure what stevia is, let us give you a brief overview. Stevia is a plant. It was discovered in Paraguay about 1,500 years ago. After its discovery, the native Guarani people used the leaves for medicinal benefits. Interestingly, they also used it to sweeten their famous herbal yerba maté tea. SweetLeaf Stevia has zero calories, zero carbs, and is non glycemic. Doesn't stevia have a bad aftertaste? Not all stevia is created equal. The bitter aftertaste that can be experienced from other products may have arisen from artificial ingredients or chemicals used in processing. SweetLeaf Stevia has no bitterness or aftertaste. Are SweetLeaf products appropriate for people with diabetes? Yes, SweetLeaf Stevia products, with their non-glycemic response, are appropriate for people with diabetes. We advise anyone with medical questions or specific health conditions to check with their physician for medical recommendations. Next page

We have our own factory and a large number of skilled jewelry craftsmen who set, plate, polish and shape jewelry in order to make sure it meets the highest standards Wear Your Birthstone The custom of wearing gems as a symbol of luck and good health is ancient. In Europe they used to wear gemstones according to the month of birth at the beginning of the 15th century. It goes further back in time to the Biblical story of the 12 Breastplate Stones. Birthstones are used as an Amulet of Healing Power that brings Luck, Protection, Good Health, Fertility, Purity, Happiness and Strength. A Great Gift For Mother's Day, Father’s Day, Wedding, Birthday, Graduation Anniversary Day, Valentine's Day or Christmas Day and New Years. Jewelry Care At the end of the day, take your jewelry off and put it in your gift box. Don't wear it while bathing, swimming or sleeping. Avoid direct contact with perfumes, body washes, lotions and excessive sweating. Don't expose to the sun or avoid high temperature. Clean jewelry with a soft cloth before putting away. Store your jewelry separately to prevent bumping into each other and causing tiny scratches. title: Garmin dezlCam LMTHD 6in Truck Navigator w/ Dash Cam plus Lifetime Map Updates (010-N1457-00) - (Renewed)
text: Product Description Garmin's First Truck Navigator with Built-in Dash Cam All-in-one 6. 0-inch trucking navigator with premium navigation features and built-in dash cam that serves as your eyewitness on the road Detailed maps of North America, plus free lifetime map updates Custom truck routing for the size and weight of your truck Truck & Trailer Services Directory, plus points of interest (POIs) highly-rated by truckers Route warnings, including sharp curves, bridge heights, weight limits, steep grades and more Built-in Dash Cam Helpful Road Warnings dezlCam has detailed maps for North America that also include truck-related restrictions - like bridge heights, sharp curves, weight limits and more - and related information for most major roads and highways. Customized Truck Routing Just enter your vehicle profile information (customizable by height, weight, length, width and hazardous materials) and find truck-preferred routes suitable for the size and weight of your truck. You can easily swap trailer sizes with the touch of a button. The onboard Trip Planner lets you create multiple-stop routes and plan and save future trips. Easy Route Shaping When you prefer to drive on certain streets or through specific towns, dezlCam lets you easily alter your drive. Easy Route Shaping lets you add one or more points to the route you see onscreen and dezlCam reconfigures the drive for you. Truck-specific POIs and Services Need help finding places to go? Locate POIs that truck drivers prefer - and have given high ratings - including truck stops, weigh stations, parking, lodging, Wi-Fi hot spots and more. You can even search and filter truck stops by brand name or by your preferred amenities, such as showers, scales, hot spot and truck wash. text: Product Description Foase Under Eye Patches About PURA D'OR PURA D’OR is driven by the desire to provide superior solutions to your toughest beauty and personal care problems. Experience nature and purity in every formula with the combination of select natural ingredients, premium essential oils, and our naturally-based preservative system. Manufactured in sunny Southern California, PURA D’OR is dedicated to providing sustainable and friendly products that use renewable energy. Foase Beauty Under Eye Patch Shine like never before with 20 Pairs of Under Eye Patch with Real 24K Gold Tired of tired eyes? Don’t worry, feeling and looking young is now made easy with PURA D’OR Foase Under Eye Patches. Diminish the appearance of dark circles, puffy eye bags, fine lines, and signs of fatigued eyes. With collagen, minerals, and real 24K Gold, Foase Under Eye Patches help revitalize and rejuvenate your under-eye skin to leave you looking youthful and awake. Made with Real 24K Gold Reduces the appearance of the fine lines, wrinkles, crow’s feet Refreshes & de-puffs under-eye bags Helps prevent and reduce premature signs of aging Read more Our Approach Rare, Exotic Ingredients We use hand-selected rare botanical ingredients that are imported from different parts of the world to give you the highest quality. Purity in a Bottle We take pride in using ingredients that are friendlier to your skin and nature always has a special place in our hearts. With compliance and respect to our mission, we give you purity in every PURA D'OR bottle. All of our products are free from sulfates, parabens, silicones, and other artificial additives. Cruelty-Free Our products are not just harsh-free and Vegan-friendly, but it is also cruelty-free. Our products are not tested on animals. No third-party testings. In-House Manufacturing Our products are manufactured in our U.S. facility with adherence to our strict quality control system to meet and exceed industry and government standards. Because of this, it is more prone to early signs of aging like puffiness, discoloration, fine lines, wrinkles, and more. Real 24K Gold helps boost the production of collagen to your skin to help smoothen your skin and soothe tired, puffy eyes. Read more Benefits of Using Foase Eye Rejuvenating Masque Bring the Spa to Your House Comes with 20 easy-to-use under-eye patches that you can use in your own convenience. Keep it in the fridge before application to the under eye for a much more relaxing and cooling effect. Brighten the Appearance of Under Eye Dark Circles The blend of ingredients and 24K Colloidal Gold helps reduce puffiness, bags, crow’s feet, and tired eyes. Reduce Signs of Aging The moisturizing benefits of the under-eye mask stimulates regeneration and rejuvenation of tired skin under your eyes to smoothen and reduce the appearance of wrinkles, fine lines, and other signs of aging. text: From the brand At Ejis, our goal is to protect you from sweat stains, yellow marks, and odor, giving you what we like to call Wearable Confidence. Our story How we got our start We wanted to help a friend who didn't get a promotion because of his excessive sweat. After testing countless products, we created our first sweat proof undershirt for him. It worked so well that he secured a job at a competing firm. That's when we knew we had to share what we had made. What makes our product unique We care about the success of our customers which is why we made our products to work in all situations. Using never-fail sweat proof material, silver odor-fighting technology, and high quality fabric, our products will stay effective even after being washed and dried 50+ times. Why we love what we do Every week we get emails from customers telling us how their lives are better because of our products. Hearing those stories and knowing we played a part in helping them feeling more confident is why we do what we do. title: Alba Botanica Sensitive Sunscreen Spray, SPF 50, Fragrance Free, 6 Oz
text: Product Description Protect your skin from harmful UVA and UVB rays with Alba Botanica Fragrance Free Clear Spray Sensitive SPF 50 Sunscreen. Our lightweight, air-powered mist is made with botanical ingredients such as chamomile and aloe for a smooth finish without a heavy or greasy feeling. This sunscreen is recommended by the Skin Cancer Foundation and is water resistant for up to 80 minutes. Our formula is made with 100% vegetarian ingredients, and it does not contain any oxybenzone, octinoxate, synthetic fragrances or gluten. It's also biodegradable and not tested on animals. Includes one 6 oz. bottle of Alba Botanica Fragrance Free Clear Spray Sensitive SPF 50 Sunscreen. We’re dedicated to making high quality, 100% vegetarian products that overflow with botanical ingredients. We also exclude all cruelly obtained animal ingredients. *see ingredients list Paraben Free We believe in using natural ingredients that help treat skin, not by using harmful chemicals like parabens. While parabens are found in skin care products to help lengthen shelf-life, they can cause long term health problems. That’s why none of Alba Botanica products use any type of parabens. To honor that vision, we created a vibrant line of body-loving products that nourish the skin, hair, and of course, the soul. Whether we’re creating a fan favorite formula or working on the next big thing, we’re dedicated tomaking high quality, 100% vegetarian products that overflow with botanical ingredients. From the choices we make in the field to the final products we put on shelves, we aim to help fellow women look beautiful on the outside while feeling beautiful on the inside. title: Plant Therapy Thyme Linalool Essential Oil 10 mL (1/3 oz) 100% Pure, Undiluted, Therapeutic Grade
text: From the brand Join the Plant Therapy family! Previous page Next page Product Description Plant Therapy Thyme Linalool Essential Oil Thyme Linalool's fresh, herbaceous aroma is perfect for diffusing around the house and creating a soothing atmosphere. To use aromatically, diffuse using 2-3 drops per 100 mL of water. Thyme Linalool is a gentle oil that can be used in DIY facial and body care. Its woody, herbaceous scent makes it an excellent oil for supporting healthy respiration and it's also known to help aid digestion. This oil can also be used in body care DIYs to help with digestion. To use topically, dilute to a maximum of 4% in your favorite carrier and gently massage in a clockwise motion on the abdomen. Read more KidSafe Essential Oil Blends KidSafe by Plant Therapy is the first-ever line of essential oils developed especially for children. Formulated by Robert Tisserand for children ages 2–10, KidSafe features a variety of synergies and single oils targeted for common issues in this age range. All are available as 100% pure, undiluted essential oils as well as pre-diluted roll-ons.As parents ourselves, the Plant Therapy team wouldn’t settle for anything less than absolute safety, and these oils aren’t just 100% safe for children, they’re effective too! Single Essential Oils Any single essential oil is a concentrated, volatile, aromatic liquid that is obtained from the fruits, seeds, flowers, bark, stems, roots, leaves or other parts of a plant.There are estimated to be 10,000 aromatic plants (ie that contain essential oils) on Earth, and about 500 of these are processed commercially for essential oil extraction. These oils have been used for centuries for both their healing and aromatic benefits, and Plant Therapy offers over 100 single essential oils, perfect for all your aromatherapy needs. Essential Oil Blends A synergy, or blend, of essential oils is the combination of two or more single oils to produce a combined effect greater than the sum of their separate effects. Plant Therapy Synergies are all tried- and-tested formulations.Any successful Plant Therapy essential oil blend must meet our 4 criteria: It needs to work, It needs to be safe, It needs to smell appealing & It needs to be affordable! Pre-Diluted Roll-Ons A synergy, or blend, of essential oils is the combination of two or more single oils to produce a combined effect greater than the sum of their separate effects. Plant Therapy Synergies are all tried- and-tested formulations.Plant Therapy offers these 100% pure essential oils diluted in our Fractionated Coconut Oil, in ready-to-use roll-on bottles that are the perfect on-the-go essential oil use. KidSafe Blends Single Oils Synergy Blends Roll-Ons Read more At Plant Therapy we strive to stay on the cutting-edge of Aromatherapy safety and education. We strive to set a standard for safety and transparency in the industry, continue to educate our customers and share up-to-date information with every member of our staff. We take great pride in making sure our oils are safe, pure and natural. All of our oils are 100% pure therapeutic grade. Our oils are unadulterated, free of synthetics and entirely pure. Plant Therapy has certified aromatherapists on staff who are always continuing their education and available for customer concerns. Our aromatherapists contribute to our educational and DIY blog posts. Read more Read more

title: HIFI WALKER H2, High Resolution Bluetooth MP3 Player, DSD DAC, Portable Digital Audio Music Player with 32GB Memory Card, Support Up to 256GB
text: Product Description High Performance Decoder Delivers in depth, detailed and distortion-free high resolution audio using the famous, proven Texas Instruments Burr Brown PCM5102 DAC. This with the Rockchip Nano D Dual core micro controller offers a stable system with no jitter. Enjoy DSD Playback: Experience the natural sound and intense detail of DSD audio formats, thanks to the high-quality digital audio, it can reach 64 times the CD audio sampling rate. Line-Output The line output allows connection to another amplifier such as an in home audio system and vehicle audio system. USB OTG The SD card slot and OTG feature enables unlimited expansion with other cards and USB type C flash drives. USB type C-OTG cable not included. USB-DAC Under USB-DAC mode, the player can be used as a computer decoding amp 2-way Bluetooth 4.2 Streaming with AptX Technology Experience enhanced high-definition wireless audio output from HIFI WALKER H2 via Bluetooth 4.2 with Qualcomm aptX technology. Customized Equalizer (EQ) Rock / Classic / Jazz / Pop / Dance / Vocal / Blues / Heavy Metal / Customize etc. Supported Audio File Format DSF (2.8MHz/ 1bit) (DSD) DFF (2.8MHz/ 1bit)(DSD) WAV (192KHz/64bit) APE (192KHz/24 bit) FLAC（192KHz/24bit） MP3（48KHz/16bit） WMA (192KHz/24bit) OGG(48KHz/16bit) Aif（Aiff） (384KHz/32 bit) AAC（48KHz/16bit） HIFI WALKER H2 Bluetooth MP3 Player FAQ for HIFIWALKER H2 1. How to transfer music to H2? Download music to computer firstly, using the micro usb cable to connect mp3 player and computer, after the mp3 player is recognized by computer, you could copy the music that downloaded from computer to the mp3 player. 2. Why I can't feel the real hifi sound when I connect my cheap headphone? The H2 support DSD high resoltion music format, you need to connect professional wired headphone or speaker system, then you can feel the hifi sound. 3.How can I use USB DAC function? First switch the USB mode to USB DAC mode on the H2 (Enter the setting menu to switch USB mode to select DAC). and then connect the H2 to the computer via USB and use it as USB DAC. Please Note: In DAC mode, H2 can not display the disk name on computer. If need drag and drop file, please switch back to the USB mode on H2. 4.Can this player work with iTunes? Is it compatible? No, unfortunately it is NOT compatible with iTunes. This functions more like an external hard drive. You simply plug it in, an option to open it as a folder pops up, and you simply drag and drop your music. 5.How to connect Bluetooth headphone/speaker to the H2? Please make sure that the Bluetooth headphone/speaker is in pairing mode (make sure the device is disconnected from any external bluebooth device). When the Bluetooth headphone/speaker is in pairing mode, turn on Bluetooth on the H2 and search for the bluetooth headphone/speaker to connect. High performance decoder Delivers in depth, detailed and distortion-free high resolution audio using the famous, proven Texas Instruments Burr Brown PCM5102 DAC with low energy consumption for extended battery life. Wired quality sound,wirelessly Experience enhanced high-definition wireless audio output from HIFI WALKER H2 via Bluetooth 4.2 with Qualcomm aptX technology. Receives & amplifies music from your smart phone via Bluetooth. Due to the compact dimensions of the player, your hand and walls may affect the Bluetooth range. Supports all popular files Whether you listen to new files in premium high resolution audio formats, or your favorite MP3 tracks, there are no restrictions when it comes to making the perfect playlist with HIFI WALKER H2. The playback hours for different files is for reference only. Many factors will affect the result.Your experience maybe longer or shorter. Read more Drag & Drop Without pre-installing tons of apps to sync your favorite music, simply drag & drop the audio files into H2 folder. It is that easy. Flexible usage options The line output allows connection to another amplifier such as an in home audio system. Convenient usage with vehicle audio system. USB-C OTG & Digital output The Micro SD card slot and OTG feature enables unlimited expansion with other cards and USB flash drives. USB Type C-OTG cable not included. No internal fixed capacity storage. Capacity of individual card or USB flash drive is currently limited to 256 GB (approximately 300 albums of flac files) System can handle up to 14,999 files. Digital (optical) audio output supported. USB Type C-digital output adapter needed (not included). Read more Aviation grade metarial High-grade zinc alloy chassis lends the player its unique natural to receive ultimate touching experience and sturdy protection. Navigates with scroll wheel Simplifying your control intuitively to your thumb with the awesome scroll wheel. The scroll wheel controls Play/Pause, Next, Previous, and Volumn increase/decrease. Enable Blind Control with Physical Buttons on each side Small size Size smaller than a deck of cards. Easily slides into any pocket Read more Specifications Model: H2 Dimensions: 90*55*15mm Product Weight: 152g Display: 2.0 Inches 320*240 TFT Display Battery: 1300mAH/3.7V Li-ion Battery. How to transfer music to H2? Download music to computer firstly, using the micro usb cable to connect mp3 player and computer, after the mp3 player is recognized by computer, you could copy the music that downloaded from computer to the mp3 player. 2. Why I can't feel the real hifi sound when I connect my cheap headphone? The H2 support DSD high resoltion music format, you need to connect professional wired headphone or speaker system, then you can feel the hifi sound. 3.How can I use USB DAC function? First switch the USB mode to USB DAC mode on the H2 (Enter the setting menu to switch USB mode to select DAC). and then connect the H2 to the computer via USB and use it as USB DAC. Please Note: In DAC mode, H2 can not display the disk name on computer. If need drag and drop file, please switch back to the USB mode on H2. 4.Can this player work with iTunes? Is it compatible? No, unfortunately it is NOT compatible with iTunes. This functions more like an external hard drive. You simply plug it in, an option to open it as a folder pops up, and you simply drag and drop your music. 5.How to connect Bluetooth headphone/speaker to the H2? Please make sure that the Bluetooth headphone/speaker is in pairing mode (make sure the device is disconnected from any external bluebooth device). When the Bluetooth headphone/speaker is in pairing mode, turn on Bluetooth on the H2 and search for the bluetooth headphone/speaker to connect. title: VTech BC8312 Wyatt The Whale Storytelling Baby Sleep Soother with a White Noise Sound Machine Featuring; 10 Stories, 10 Ambient Sounds & 10 Calming Melodies with Glow-on-Ceiling Night Light
text: Product Description The BC8312 Wyatt the Whale Storytelling Baby Sleep Soother comes ready with 10 calming lullabies and 10 soft ambient sounds, like a trickling stream and white noise, to help baby relax.Choose from 10 stories and help baby drift off to dreamland. A gentle voice reads new and classic tales for up to 40 minutes of story time. Soft light shines through the top of Wyatt's back, projecting a starry night scene onto the ceiling. Plus, you can choose from 3 relaxing colors to help baby sleep. Download the VTech Wyatt app and connect to your mobile device using Wi-Fi. The app lets you swap out stories, songs and sounds with just a few taps to soothe baby night after night. Help baby feel close to you even when you can't be there by recording your own voice for them to doze off to. Find a script in the free app, or calm your little one by making up a story of your own.Set the soother to shut off after 30, 45 or 60 minutes so you don't have to sneak into the nursery once baby is asleep. title: Peepers by PeeperSpecs Cooper Rectangular Blue Light Blocking Reading Glasses
text: From the brand Previous page WE ARE FAMILY - Peepers is a 4th generation family-run company that is continuously reinventing the spectacle and we have fun doing it! Our company began with a quest to find upbeat eyewear, and that light-hearted spirit is embedded in everything we do. Our family's legacy is dedicated to the pursuit of fashion at its most fun. Our History - We have come a long way from our start as an importer and distributor of scissors, shears, and fine cutlery. Sammann Company Inc. was first established in 1908 and founded the Peepers Brand in 1993 when Mrs. Sammann, a.k.a. Mz. Peepers recognized a need for fashionable readers and began designing the fun looks that started Peepers. Today that same passion has carried on as we continue to create stylish, optical quality reading and sunglasses. Peepers Fun Fact - Our eyewear has been featured six times as one of Oprah's Favorite Things! Steps Toward A Brighter Future - Investing in generations to come is important to us. We hope to continue to make an impact by giving back to our communities through local volunteer work and community outreach initiatives like our Peepers for Teachers Program. Designing With Intention & Sustainability - We see the beauty and importance in natural, sustainable materials and challenge ourselves to integrate them into our collections each season. We are also proud to utilize solar power as our main source of energy at our headquarters. Find Your Perfect Peepers! Visit the Store Next page From the manufacturer Pursuing the Beauty of Self-Expression Through Eyewear! Peepers fashion-forward eyewear is available in multiple color options and various reading magnification strengths as well as just simply no correction Blue Light to provide protection and style. Why Peepers? Reading & No Correction Blue Light Focus Lens - Blue Light Filtering technology that provides UV400 Protection and filters over 40% of high-energy visible blue light¹ to help prevent symptoms of digital eye strain.² Quality, Style & Comfort You Can Clearly See - From exceptional lens technology to a comfortable fit, we've paired trend-setting style with innovative features to help enhance the way we live and work in the digital world. For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear. title: MusicNomad The Nomad String, Body, & Hardware Cleaning Tool (MN205)
text: Product Description Our patented, innovative design both extends the life and preserves the tone of strings & cleans the body & hardware without any cleaning solutions. The premium quality washable microfiber pad cleans on top AND underneath guitar strings in seconds. The 100% lint free microfiber pad protects frets and fretboard from getting damaged while at the same time cleaning them. Also, the microfiber pad quickly cleans dust, grime and fingerprints on the instrument’s body and hard to reach areas. Turn it around to use the super soft brush fibers as a cleaner for dust buildup and care on the body, bridge, pickups, saddles, tuners, headstock and more. Cleaning off dust & grime is a must do before you apply any polish to avoid scratching the finish. The All in 1 Nomad Tool can be used on all electric and acoustic stringed instruments, drums, mixers, computers, pedals and more. text: From the manufacturer About Us For more than two decades, Perricone MD has been a holistic, three-tier skincare and wellness system. This consists of diet, essential dietary supplements and potent topical skincare solutions backed by powerful ingredients, cutting-edge research and extensive clinical and consumer studies. Perricone MD was created by Dr. Nicholas Perricone, world-renowned author of New York Times bestseller, The Wrinkle Cure. Dr. Perricone’s seminal work challenged the prevailing norms of the skincare industry with its visionary approach to aging and introduction to the advantages of a healthy lifestyle. Perricone MD is driven by the pursuit of fearless innovation and a stubbornly uncompromising spirit of excellence. Good enough has never been good enough—a belief that drives our commitment to consistently deliver targeted results. We continuously seek the truth in unlocking the powerful science behind healthy-looking skin, from the inside-out and outside-in. title: Offenbach: Orphee Aux Enfers La Belle Helene La Grande-duchesse de Gerolstein
text: Editorial Reviews Marc Minkowski Offenbach: Orphée aux enfers, La Belle Hélène, La Grande-duchesse de Gérolstein (6CD) Three sparkling operettas that exemplify Offenbach's irresistible joie de vivre and biting satirical wit. All linked to theatrical productions by Laurent Pelly - a director noted for his comic flair - these recordings offer some rediscovered numbers, since they use specially-prepared editions of the scores. Marc Minkowski conducts with an inimitable and authentic sense of style, while the casts boast such singers as Natalie Dessay, Felicity Lott, Patricia Petibon, Véronique Gens, Yann Beuron, Michel Sénéchal and Laurent Naouri. title: Dr. Brown's Advantage Symmetrical Pacifier with Air Flow - Blue Glow-in-the-Dark - 3-Pack - 0-6m
text: Product Description Get the Dr. Brown's Advantage - The pacifier designed with baby's acceptance in mind! The advantage pacifier is a fully symmetrical soother, with reversible bulb that fits in baby's mouth either RIGHT-SIDE up or upside down. The 100% silicone bulb is soft but sturdy, using a rounded shape that satisfies baby's suckling reflex. A unique shield design reduces irritation by providing plenty of air for baby's sensitive skin to breathe. Plus, it glows in the dark - making it easy to find day or night. Advantage pacifiers grow with baby, coming in two stages to fit developing faces. Taste-free, odor-free, and BPA-free. Quickly clean in the dishwasher (top rack) or sterilize by boiling, microwave, or electric sterilizer. title: Tender Leaf Toys - Hungry Wooden Tortoise Shape Sorter Toy - Encourages Imaginative Play, Improves Recognition and Problem Solving Skills - 3 Years +
text: Product Description Tender Leaf Toys - Hungry Wooden Tortoise Shape Sorter Toy - Encourages Imaginative Play, Improves Recognition and Problem Solving Skills - 3 Years + As all of our Tender Leaf Toys the Hungry Wooden Tortoise Shape Sorter provides a start to spark imagination in all children so they can discover themselves, their passions, and their purpose. The Hungry Wooden Tortoise Shape Sorter encourages imaginative play and helps your child learn how to interact with others while playing. It also helps your child develop and hone fine motor skills and encourages problem solving skills. The set features 5 bright warm colored delicious colored shapes. Also includes a lid atop the tortoise which can be lifted to start all over again. Like all other Tender Leaf Toy products the Hungry Wooden Tortoise Shape Sorter allows us to show that we care about children’s future and the future of our planet. All of our toys are made from sustainable rubberwood and for every tree that becomes a beautiful toy, another is replanted. Tender leaf toys creates gentle, beautifully designed toys that promote learning through play. Our Toys traditional in concept but contemporary in design and all our products are made with a distinct focus on craftsmanship and quality. Designed in the UK, all of our products start with original sketches before they are sampled and then coloured and finally tested. With our unique blend of soft cotton fabric, gentle non toxic water stain combined with sustainable rubber wood / high quality plywood, Tender Leaf Toys make the perfect gift and look stylish around the modern playroom or nursery. We place a strong focus on child development - physical, social, creative and imaginative play are integral to all our products. We test for ages 18 months and 3 years + Our manufacturing processes, starting from cutting, painting and drying of the wood, are all undertaken at the same factory location in Indonesia. Designed in the UK, all of our products start with original sketches before they are sampled and then coloured and finally tested. With our unique blend of soft cotton fabric, gentle non toxic water stain combined with sustainable rubber wood / high quality plywood, Tender Leaf Toys make the perfect gift and look stylish around the modern playroom or nursery. We place a strong focus on child development - physical, social, creative and imaginative play are integral to all our products. We test for ages 18 months and 3 years + Our manufacturing processes, starting from cutting, painting and drying of the wood, are all undertaken at the same factory location in Indonesia.

title: Foraging Field Reference Bandana with 12 Common Edible, Medicinal, and Useful North American Plants, Trees, and Fungus Found in Nature - 100% Cotton Made in the USA
text: Product Description A FIELD REFERENCE AND FORAGING TOOL Foraging is an art that's all but lost in today's modern society, but it can make a huge difference in your life. A foraging tool like this bandana is meant to give a person power over their situation, leading to purpose, and the ability to self-aid and self-rescue. Read more The Foraging Bandana was designed in cooperation with some of the finest foraging instructors. We designed this bandana to act as a learning primer, field aid, and emergency reference It lists the 12 most common plants/fungus of North America, including their common and scientific names. The field uses of all 12 plants/fungus are listed using part indicator icons on each plant illustration. The bandana also includes the ”5 Steps of Identifying Edible Plants” by Samuel Thayer and ”Rules and Ethics of Foraging” by Mark "Merriwether" Vorderbruggen. Read more For neophytes, this bandana serves as a fun, stepping-stone educational tool. For more experienced foragers, this bandana should encourage impromptu foraging, help in sharing the passion of foraging with others, demonstrate alignment with the foraging lifestyle, and help promote awareness of continued education in this field. We worked with experts, Mark "Merriwether" Vorderbruggen and Dr. Nicole Apelian to choose plants based on the following criteria: Abundance in USA Ease of Identification Few or no poisonous look-alikes Ability to represent on a bandana Ease to process into its usable form Read more

title: ZEISS Victory Pocket 10x25 Black Binoculars
text: Product Description Whether you are strolling in the park or on a long walking tour, you can always enjoy birdwatching and observing the natural world. With this featherweight giant in pocket-sized format, the Victory Pocket offers you high-performance binoculars from ZEISS for virtually all observation situations. Despite their amazingly light-weight construction, their high magnification and FL-lenses with ZEISS T* multi-layer coating help them to deliver brilliant image quality. The LotuTec coating that ensures that water drips right off them and dirt can be removed without a trace. Technical data: Magnification: 8 xEffective lens diameter: 25 mmExit pupil diameter: 3. 1 mmTwilight factors: 14. 1Field of view at 1. 000 m: 130 mApparent field of view: 60 °Close focus: 1. 9 mDiopter adjustment range: +3 | -3 dptExit pupil distance: 16. 5 mmLens type: FLPrismSystem: Schmidt-PechanLotuTec / Nitrogen filling: yes / yesWater resistance: 100 mbar Thanks to their lightweight and compact format these binoculars even fit in a small jacket pocket, and are so light that you will hardly know they are there. The new Victory Pocket promise high performance in all kinds of outdoor applications. title: Waterproof Pet Feeding Mat, Anti-Slip Water Bowl Mat with Raised Edges to Prevent Spills, Large 22" x 14" Tray Designed to Protect Your Floors, Dishwasher Safe Silicone Dog Bowl Mat
text: Product Description Pets can be messy eaters, getting food and water spills all over the place! We all love our pets, but no one enjoys a messy floor. Avisiony offers the finest quality silicone mat to protect your floors! Our mat keeps your floors clean and dry since the edge lip is taller than other mats. Pet food and water messes can be a thing of the past and it is very easy to clean up - throw it in the dishwasher, wash it in the sink, or just hose it off. This mat is exceptionally durable and will provide you with years of use. Ideal for any living space, even tiny apartments Compact size that fits practically anywhere Raised edge & waterproof material stop water & food from spilling Simple design & neutral color to blend into any decoration. Light weight & flexibility for easy cleaning & storage Washes with ease in sink or dishwasher Read more Highest Quality Pet Food Mat To Keep Your Floor Clean! KEEP YOUR FLOOR CLEAN AND PROTECTED Have the food bits and water slops self-contained with this pet food mat, protecting your polished, tiled, hardwood floors or carpets from spillages with our large pet mats! YOUR IDEAL SIZE At 22" x 14" our silicone mat is lightly bigger than other placemats to easily accommodate water and food bowls. With an increased outer lip height to catch crumbles and spills, it stays put and holds elevated feeder or stand-alone dishes in place due to its texture. TALL EDGES Tall Edges – Our edge lip is taller than other mats to keep food and water from spilling on your floor. Also the surface has raised dots to keep food and water bowls in place to reduce the risk of accidental tips and spills. EASY TO CLEAN & STORE A quick water rinse or running it through the dishwasher will fresh it again! Lighter, flexible and portable, this pet placemat, simply roll it up to restore it or pack it for travel in order to save space! Read more Safe Food Grade Silicone Keeps Your Pet Safe Made of sturdy non-toxic silicone, the Avisiony feeding mat is perfectly safe for your pet, this non-allergenic mat for food and water bowls is non-toxic and good for our environment. title: Vive Fall Mat - Bedside Fall Safety Protection Mat for Elderly, Senior, Handicap - Prevention Pad Reduce Risk of Injury from Impact - Prevent Bed Falling - Anti Fatigue, Standing Non Slip
text: Product Description Bedside Fall Mat by Vive Providing bedside protection for those at risk of falling, the Vive bedside fall mat is constructed with a high-density, high-impact absorbing foam. Slip resistant mat stays securely in place, while beveled, low profile edges allow for easy access for wheelchairs and other mobility aids. Reduces Bedside Injuries: Supplying complete bedside coverage, the full-length mat ensures optimal bedside safety for loved ones or patients at risk of falling. The high-impact absorption foam padding reduces head injuries and other bodily damage due to falling from the bed. High-Impact Absorption Foam: Absorbing the impact of falls, the soft, high-density foam also provides safe and secure footing for patients, loved ones and caregivers. The waterproof the bedside fall mat is easily cleaned to help maintain a healthy bedside environment. Beveled Edges for Easy Access: Minimizing tripping hazards, the bedside fall mat has low-profile, beveled edges to also provide easy access for wheelchairs and other mobility aids. A durable, slip-resistant rubber backing prevents the mat from sliding on any floor surface, including wood, tile or carpet. The soft foam mat has a non-slip, textured cover to provide safe and comfortable footing around the bed. Dimensions: Length: 72” Width: 24” Height: ⅞”

title: Bundle - 5 Items - Clipper Lighter Reggae"Rasta" Collection with Rolling Paper Depot"Rasta" Rolling Tray
text: Product Description CLIPPER is not just any lighter - it's unique, eco-friendly, multi-purpose device. CLIPPER was the first original refillable lighter and has been made in Barcelona, Spain since 1972. It's unique round shape and the special functions have made it popular in over 80 countries and is the Worlds #1 selling lighter. CLIPPER is a high tech quality lighter that comes in multiple designs for all kinds of enthusiasts. CLIPPER Lighters are obviously used to light cigarettes and many other items but also can be used for: 1) Packing tobacco in your hand-rolled cigarettes with the patented removable flint system. 2) Can be used to pack the tobacco inside pipes. 3) Placed perfectly inside beer bottles to keep your bottle from getting mixed up. 4) Opening beer bottles. These are just the more popular things CLIPPER lighters are used for, but your imagination is the limit. All over the world there are people with amazing CLIPPER Lighter collections and everyday there are new collectors starting out due to the wide variety of designs that CLIPPER has to offer. Start your collection today and join the rest of the world in "Clipper Mania" Rolling Paper Depot "Rasta" Rolling Tray The Rolling Paper Depot rolling trays serve their purpose perfectly. This rolling tray is perfect size. Big enough to hold your supplies yet small enough to be a travel companion. The edges are designed with extra height and rounded corners to ensure no tobacco gets stuck anywhere. Grab your favorite pack of rolling papers, a good blend of filler, and this rolling tray and start making some smokes. title: Truform Sheer Compression Stockings, 15-20 mmHg, Women's Knee High Length, 20 Denier
text: From the manufacturer What compression level is right for you? 8-15 mmHg Mild pressure, used for proactive leg health — Compression strength for preventative care. 15-20 mmHg Moderate pressure, common starting point for first time wear — Compression strength for minor conditions. 20-30 mmHg Firm pressure, typically used when recommended by a certified fitter or healthcare provider — Compression strength for pronounced medical symptoms. 30-40 mmHg Extra-Firm pressure, used only when prescribed by a doctor — Compression strength for severe medical conditions. Higher compression levels will impact fit and may create a false impression that size is too small. Always confirm your correct compression level prior to fitting. Higher levels of compression are harder to apply and remove. Users with limited strength should choose a lower level of compression. Measuring Instructions Ankle : Measure ankle circumference at the smallest part of the ankle, right above the ankle bone. Calf : Measure calf circumference around the fullest part of the calf Measuring Tips Measure first thing in the morning when swelling or edema is minimal. Take firm measurements without depressing the skin. Keep measuring tape in a level position and note measurements at each point. Read more Read more Moderate 15-20 mmHg Strength Recommended for : Minor Varicose Veins, Minor Spider Veins, Edema, DVT, Post-Surgery, Swelling in Ankles Calf Feet, Enlarged Bulging Veins, Pregnant Nursing Expecting Mothers (when recommended by a doctor), Travel (prevents blood pooling and clots in frequent flyers), Tired Aching Legs, Muscle Recovery Post Cardio Workout and Exercise. Beauty Shaping and Leg Contouring. Features & Benefits Fashionable Sheer Kni t - 20 denier dress nylon hose for casual, business, or formal wear. Stay-up Top - Lined with silicone grip ensures stocking remains in place throughout the day. Knit-In Heel - Defined, reinforced heel pocket adds durability and provides orientation for anatomical fit. Comfort Toe - Roomy closed toe box will not compress toes and eliminates pressure and chaffing on sensitive feet. Graduated Compression - Pressure is greatest at the ankle and decreases gradually up the leg to promote healthy circulation. title: Nikon W300 Waterproof Underwater Digital Camera with TFT LCD, 3", Yellow (26525)
text: Product Description Show the world what you're made of. Some people are happy to take pictures from the comfort of the sidelines. That's nice. But if you want to be part of the action, you need a camera as tough as you. For those thrill seekers and action-hounds, meet the COOLPIX W300, a tough-as-nails camera designed for the extremes. Waterproof, freeze proof, shockproof and dustproof, it captures 4K Ultra HD video, 16 MP photos, time-lapse movies and more in the harshest conditions. Bring it surfing, skiing, SCUBA diving, biking, climbing...wherever your adventures lead. Use the built-in GPS, eCompass, altimeter, Wi-Fi and Bluetooth Low Energy to track and share every heart-pounding moment. Show the world what you're really made of. Use the built-in GPS, eCompass, altimeter, Wi-Fi(R) and Bluetooth(R) Low Energy to track and share every heart-pounding moment. Show the world what you're really made of. Read more Ready for Adventure Waterproof to 100 ft. Take it snorkeling, Scuba diving, fishing or just having fun in the pool. Freezeproof to 14° Take it skiing, snowboarding, sledding, snow shoeing or ice skating. Shockproof Can handle rough conditions, including drops from up to 7.9 ft. high. Dustproof Take it to the beach, the ball field...any place that gets dirty. Read more Jaw-dropping Photos and Videos 16-MP Backside Illuminated CMOS Sensor. Share epic photos and videos that put your friends and family in the moment. The COOLPIX W300's 16 MP low-light sensor and fast f/2.8 NIKKOR zoom lens freeze action in striking detail, even when the light is fading. It's fast autofocus and continuous shooting speed helps you land shots others might miss. Turn on Macro Mode and reveal hidden details in flowers, plants, insects and more. Zoom into the Action 5x Optical Zoom NIKKOR Lens with Hybrid VR. When the action is just out of reach, zoom in with the telephoto power of the COOLPIX W300's 5x optical zoom lens. You'll have the flexibility to get the whole scene into the frame or to zoom in for a tight view. The whole time you're shooting, Nikon's Hybrid VR (Vibration Reduction) keeps your photos and videos steady, even when the road gets bumpy. 4K Ultra HD Videos with Stereo Sound* With the touch of a button, the COOLPIX W300 records 4K Ultra HD or 1080p Full HD videos with stereo sound. Combine your favorite clips into a 30-second compilation with background music and special effects using Short Movie Show—ideal for sharing online. Use Time-lapse recording to condense an hour of action into a 10-second sequence, or speed up time with a Superlapse video. You can even shoot stills while recording video. The camera also features VR during movie recording (5-axis hybrid: lens-shift type and electronic type) and AE lock is now available when shooting underwater video. *Not all video features are available when recording in 4K UHD, please refer to the owner’s manual for details. Action-Friendly Control Simple, Smart Operation Designed for Action. Operating the COOLPIX W300 couldn't be easier. An extra large grip and smart button placement make for stable one-handed shooting. The large 3.0-inch LCD has an anti-reflective coating for shooting in bright light. A dedicated Tool button gives you quick access to GPS, eCompass and other tools. When you're wearing heavy gloves, you can change modes simply by moving the camera. Read more Access and Share on the Go Built-in Wi-Fi and Bluetooth. Pull out a compatible smartphone or tablet to automatically transfer, review and share your photos, add caption text and even take pictures remotely with the COOLPIX W300. The Nikon SnapBridge app can automatically back-up your photos to Nikon Image Space as you shoot them. Share the moment while it's still happening. Onboard GPS, eCompass, Altimeter, Depth Gauge and More Easily track and view your course, steps taken, altitude, depth—even atmospheric and water pressure—with the COOLPIX W300. Built-in Bright LED Light Whether you're illuminating a subject or trying to see your map, the COOLPIX W300's bright LED light will come in handy. Point and Shoot Ease The COOLPIX W300 takes the work out of great photos and videos. When you're in a challenging situation, just select from 20 common Scene Modes like Night Landscape or Portrait, or choose Scene Auto Selector and let the camera choose for you. Read more

title: Bloch Dance Ballet Hair Accessories Kit
text: Product Description The bloch hair kit is a must have accessory! it's easy to use and transport and includes all your bun making essentials. Product Description The bloch hair kit is a must have accessory! it's easy to use and transport and includes all your bun making essentials.From the manufacturer It all started with a promise… ...to make the most comfortable dance shoes in the world. Read more Jacob Bloch, a shoe maker by trade, emigrated to Australia in 1930 during the height of The Great Depression. Jacob's love of music and dancing took him to the local ballet schools and at one of these schools he noticed a young dancer struggling to stay en pointe. Jacob promised he would make her a better pair of pointe shoes to dance in, and so he did. Jacob’s reputation for making high-quality dance footwear spread rapidly. Jacob’s shoes became so well-known and sought after, that it sparked the creation of a full range of dance footwear and dance fashion products. The brand grew rapidly and over time became the BLOCH we know and love. Today, BLOCH has a reputation as one of the most trusted in the industry and is still fulfilling the promise made by its founder close to nine decades ago; "to make the most comfortable dance shoe in the world". Find out with Rainbow In My Room! See a magical rainbow come to life in your own room. Just touch the button and see a beautiful, multi-colored rainbow projected across your walls and ceiling. Turn your rainbow on one color at a time or all at once with the 2 light-up modes. Works great on a night stand or desk. Part of the Uncle Milton brand, a leader in science and educational toys since 1946! Incorporates S.T.E.M. learning as you discover how rainbows are formed, light refraction and the color spectrum. title: Grit Performance Tire Pressure Gauge (0-60 PSI) Heavy Duty, with Custom Foam Case, Chrome Caps & Valve Core Repair Tool, Rapid Air Pressure Gauge, Tire Deflators Offroad Accessories, 4x4 Tires
text: Product Description THE ULTIMATE 4X4 TIRE DEFLATOR KIT, READY IN SECONDS! Do you want to cut down on fuel costs? Do you hate going to the gas station just to check your tire pressure? Now, with one simple check that takes less than three seconds - anywhere, anytime! This Heavy-duty tire pressure gauge made for 4x4 off-road warriors, ideal 0-60 PSI range with easy-to-read glow dial, has certified ANSI B40.1 gauge, just attach it to the tire's air valve and the exact measurement will show instantaneously. SUPERIOR BUILD OUALITY FOR GUARANTEED ACCURACY With Grit Performance tire deflator, rugged, reliable & accurate, achieve quick & accurate readouts, to most improve the handling, performance & fuel efficiency of your vechicle. title: 12 Days of Christmas Festive Red 2 x 2 Resin Stone Christmas Ornament Set of 12
text: Product Description Dickson's is based in Seymour, Indiana. We offer an extensive line of over 8500 items to appeal to practically every age and style. Many of these are Dicksons exclusives, designed by our in-house development team from concept stage to the finished product. We introduce over 2800 new products every year to keep our selection fresh and reflective of today's gift-giving trends. Our production team manufactures all of the framed prints and wood plocks and also most of our bookmarks and pocket cards. The team takes great pride in building high quality products that will last for many years. Dickson's primary mission is to serve our customers by creating, manufacturing, distributing, and marketing biblically based gift items, to improve the lives of people everywhere. It is said that in medieval times, the twelve days of Christmas carol was used as a code to teach Christian concepts during periods of religious persecution; 12 Days of Christmas Ornaments are a beautiful way to remember those special meanings; Each ornament has a sculpted figure on the front side and a number that corresponds to one of the days mentioned in the famous carol. Ornament is made of resin stone with festive red finish; Back side of each ornament is engraved in gold with the Christian meaning for the number; Each features a green fabric ribbon hanger. Each ornament measures approximately 2 x 1.5 x 0.3 inches; Gift box also contains a colorful insert explaining the Christian meaning of each day. Perfect for grouped hanging display on a Christmas tree or ornament hanger for the holidays; Insert can also be used as a large bookmark. Ships in protective packaging; Entire set is beautifully gift boxed in vac tray with clear lid; Box is also perfect for storage. Product Description Dickson's is based in Seymour, Indiana. text: Product Description The iconic ignite spike less franchise has been taken to the net level! Built from the ground up with pro form TPU outsole with an organically-altered traction pattern. A full length ignite foam midsole, wrapped in sole shield for added durability, provides unparalleled comfort and energy return to help you feel and play your best all day long. The upper features a flat-knit waterproof mesh vamp with PWRFRAME reinforcement, and decoupled pwrcage pieces to provide a secure fit. The innovative materials and progressive design provide the performance you need on the course and the style you need while off It. title: Goodbye Girl, The [Blu-ray]
text: Product Description Paula McFadden knows: In romance, actors all follow the same stage instruction: Exit. Without warning, her actor boyfriend split today for a movie role and sublet their Manhattan apartment. The new tenant's name: Elliot Garfield. Profession: actor. Richard Dreyfuss and Marsha Mason deliver comedy, zingy repartee and bitter-to-best romance in The Goodbye Girl, a lustrous charmer featuring Dreyfuss' Academy Award -winning Best Actor performance.* Neil Simon's screenplay deftly combines battle-of-the-sexes appeal with an off-Broadway subplot whose scenes "are the funniest since Mel Brooks staged 'Springtime for Hitler' [in The Producers]" (Roger Ebert, Chicago Sun-Times). You'll laugh, cry and cheer. Just say hello to this magical movie. Product Description Paula McFadden knows: In romance, actors all follow the same stage instruction: Exit. title: Chandrakala Women's Indian Ethnic Banarasi Saree with Unstitched Blousepiece(1088)
text: Product Description Ethnic and beautiful - so appealing in its textured appearance and perfect in its imperfections! This gorgeous saree is woven in beautiful cotton silk blend with fekwa zari bootis and a striking contrast zari border .Beautiful zari bootis across the body of the saree in the finest fekwa weave, set against a classic zari border and pallu. Traditional and spectacular as only Banarasi can be! Delicately woven bootis and a traditional patterned border and aanchal make this saree a unique gift from Banaras. Read more Blouse Piece Fabric (Cotton Silk Blend) Silk/Cotton fabric is a blend of both fibers, combining positive characteristics of each into a single textile. A lightweight, silky and comfortable weave, silk/cotton fabric has a soft and a sturdy, silken drape. It is usually made as a primarily cotton blend . This sari is made with art silk warp and cotton weft. An elegant blouse piece of Banarasi woven in gold zari in exquisite fekwa weaving on border.You can stitch this blouse piece as per your own design style and size. Blouse piece of 80 cm which is attached at one end of the saree. Read more This saree with its beautiful palette and design inspirations, is sheer elegance in Banarasi silk. A fluid drape with time-honoured patterns for simple sophistication. Read more

title: Diapers Size 4, 58 Count - Pampers Swaddlers Overnights Disposable Baby Diapers, Super Pack (Packaging May Vary)
text: Product Description What keeps baby's skin healthy? A diaper that doesn't leave skin wet, especially overnight. That's why new Pampers Swaddlers Overnights absorb wetness better and provide up to 100% leak-proof nighttime skin protection to help keep your baby's skin healthy and protected all night long. New Swaddlers Overnights are designed with a Wrap&Protect Waistband that gently wraps around baby to help protect skin from irritation, and Wrap&Protect leg barriers that protect where leaks happen most. A restful night’s sleep starts with the right protection from wetness, which is why Swaddlers Overnights are extra absorbent to keep baby's skin dry throughout the night. Pampers LockAway Channels lock wetness away for dry, healthy skin while the BreatheFree Liner wicks away wetness, allowing baby's skin to breathe. Plus, Pampers Swaddlers Overnights are Skin Health Alliance Dermatologist Approved, hypoallergenic and free of parabens and latex,** so you can trust them to be safe and gentle on your little one’s delicate skin. Pampers Swaddlers Overnights are available in sizes 3–6 and come in eight fun nighttime prints. For trusted protection, trust Pampers, the #1 Canadian pediatrician recommended brand. **Natural RubberFrom the brand Previous page Diapers Visit the Store Wipes Visit the Store Training pants Visit the Store Deals Visit the Store Are all of the ingredients in Pampers safe for babies? Pampers diapers, wipes, and training pants are made from ingredients that are carefully tested and proven to be safe. The ingredients we use are common in most diapers and wipes and are used safely by millions of babies around the world every day. How many diapers should I change a day? In the first couple of months, you might find yourself changing diapers up to 10 times in 24 hours. Diapers should be changed whenever they are wet or soiled. Your baby will often (but not always) let you know. Next page From the manufacturer Previous page Find the Right Fit Babies come in all shapes and sizes—follow these steps for a comfortable and secure fit Front Fit The diaper should fit just under your baby’s belly button Leg Cuff Fit After the diaper is on, run two fingers just inside the leg cuffs so there is no gapping or bunching Waist & Fastening When fastened, you should just about be able to run two fingers around the waist Signs of a Good Fit No leaks and no red marks when you remove the diaper Next page Previous page Our Commitment Caring for babies is in our DNA. Our Pampers Bright Beginnings programs enable healthy development and early success for babies and families through education, hospital partnerships, and donations March of Dimes Partnership Pampers is proud to support the March of Dimes in giving every baby a fighting chance. We help provide our smallest diapers to the 1 million babies born before 28-week gestational age each year Sustainability Pampers cares for every baby and the planet they grow up in. We maintain zero manufacturing to landfill across all our plants and are committed to 100% renewable electricity by 2030 Community Donations Through ongoing donation efforts and partnerships with organizations like Feeding America and Matthew 25, Pampers strives to help babies get the bright beginnings they deserve Changing Table Access 9 out of 10 dads have used a public restroom that lacks a changing table. As part of our “Love the Change” campaign, we’re providing 5,000 changing tables for men’s restrooms across North America Hospital Support Proud to be the #1 choice of U.S. hospitals for nearly 50 years, we partner with nurses to develop skin-protecting products and support nursing education—all to help baby’s healthy development Next page Are Swaddlers Overnights good for nighttime protection? Yes! Pampers Swaddlers Overnights are extra absorbent* for dry nights. (*vs. Pampers Swaddlers diapers) What sizes are Swaddlers Overnights available in? Pampers Swaddlers Overnights are available in sizes 3 to 6. Are the ingredients in Pampers Swaddlers safe for my little one’s skin? Yes! All materials in Pampers diapers are carefully selected and thoroughly evaluated for safety and skin compatibility. Pampers is the #1 Pediatrician Recommended Brand and is free of parabens and latex.* (*Natural Rubber) How do Pampers Swaddlers help prevent leaks? Our Dual Leak-Guard Barriers gently seal around baby’s legs to help prevent leaks where they happen most. They are also designed with an ultra-soft and absorbent top sheet that wicks away wetness to help keep baby’s skin dry and healthy. What do you mean “packaging may vary”? We've recently made aesthetic changes. You may receive either package and product during this time. Rest assured your product is genuine and made by Pampers, but if you have questions please reach out to us directly.

title: Powerbuilt 26 Inch Portable Slant Front Rapid Toolbox Tiered Stairstep Tool Holders, 16 Gauge Steel, Chrome Hardware, Weather-Resistant Lockable Polymer Lid, Grey, 240111
text: Product Description For more than 38 years, Powerbuilt has offered best in class tools and equipment that deliver quality, innovation and durability to automotive professionals and enthusiasts. The Powerbuilt 26-inch slant front toolbox is a truck and job box built for harsh handling and outdoor environments. Like all Powerbuilt products, it offers the strength, precision and durability you demand. The Powerbuilt 26-inch slant front toolbox is a truck and job box built for harsh handling and outdoor environments. For work and play on the road, on the farm, in the trailer, shop and garage, this is your go-to tool box. Powerbuilt 26 in. Rapid Box Portable Slant Front Tool Box Here's a space-efficient, time-saving, portable 26-inch slant front tool box that stands up to harsh life on the road and in the shop. This truck and job box is built for harsh handling and outdoor environments. With details like fully-welded seams, premium powder-coating and chrome-plated hardware, this portable slant front toolbox might outlast you. This box holds 94 sockets, up to 50 combination wrenches, 9 screwdrivers and 19 ratchets or extensions.A removable socket tray offers even more versatility and flexibility on the job. And there's extra open storage space for the stuff that's just as important as tools. The heavy-duty polymer lid snugs down over your tools so they stay put during transportation. Once you reach the job site, unlock and lift the lid for easy access to all your tools. With a heavy-duty lock and weather-sealed lid, you can confidentially leave your tools in the box without worrying about rust or casual theft. title: ZYPPAH Anti Snoring Hybrid Oral Appliance Mouthpiece Stop Snoring Sleep Aid Solution Snore Stopper Mouth Guard Device - Made in USA, FDA Cleared - Military
text: Product Description ZYPPAH is an F DA-cleared, s elf-molded, b oil-and-bite oral appliance that is effective, safe and easy to use. What makes it an effective solution to eliminate snoring and different from every oral appliance sold, is that ZYPPAH combines two solutions to address your snoring problem which are: Supports Tongue & Opens Airway - ZYPPAH uses a patent-pending elastic that holds and stabilizes the tongue. This prevents the tongue from falling back into the throat and opens the airway during sleep. The tongue, which is a muscle, relaxes during sleep. Advances Lower Jaw - Moving the lower jaw forward from its normal position during sleep improves airflow and reduce the snoring sound. While this can be effective, there are limits to how far you can move your lower jaw. ZYPPAH is designed as a boil and bite mouth guard, so it can be custom fit to your teeth. The combination of tongue stabilization and lower jaw re-positioning makes ZYPPAH a truly innovative solution to stop your snoring. This snoring solution is comfortable , safe and effective . ZYPPAH snore stopper has a snoring strap that provides superior comfort while advancing your lower jaw for a good night's sleep. Our patented Tongue Elastic is proven in an independent clinical trial to stop snoring by addressing the root cause which is your tongue. All ZYPPAH anti snoring devices are made in the USA and are cleared by the FDA . While ZYPPAH is widely acclaimed and endorsed by celebrities , ZYPPAH is the only anti-snoring mouthpiece proven to work on NBC Nightly News , Good Morning America , DR. Oz , Bloomberg and endorsed by celebrities, including Shaquille O’Neal (SHAQ) , Steven A. Smith , Bob Eubanks and others Meet Dr. Jonathan Greenburg Inventor of the ZYPPAH Hello! I’m Dr. Jonathan Greenburg. As a dentist for over 25 years, and now as the founder CEO of ZYPPAH, I've spent my life helping patients live better.ZYPPAH is a high-growth developer of Hybrid Oral Appliances invented to solve the problem of snoring. ZYPPAH, which is “Happy Z” spelled backward, in a phrase, embodies my passion to realize a world where Happy Z’s become the norm for every individual around the world.I hope you’ll join hundreds of thousands of ZYPPAH owners to get the restful sleep you deserve. - Dr. Greenburg Our Brand Our mission is to give everyone great sleep every night of their lives. Join the thousands of happy customers! Scientific innovation is the cornerstone of what we do, and we're constantly improving our products Read more TAKE YOUR TIME Wear your ZYPPAH one hour before sleeping the first night, but take your time to get used to it and the experience will gradually improve. The more you wear your mouthpiece while awake, the faster you’ll become accustomed to it. DIFFICULTY FALLING ASLEEP If you’re having trouble sleeping, just remove your ZYPPAH and go back to sleep. Each night that goes by should allow you to sleep longer with the appliance, after a few weeks you’ll get used to it. EXCESSIVE DROOLING You may experience excess salivation because your brain thinks you just put a lot of food in your mouth. If so, wear your ZYPPAH one hour before bed and get distracted, your brain will realize that this isn’t food and the salivation will eventually stop. Read more Original Military Ghost Pink Beauty Sleep Z-Factor Patented Technology ✓ ✓ ✓ ✓ ✓ Self-Molded & Custom Fit ✓ ✓ ✓ ✓ ✓ FDA Cleared ✓ ✓ ✓ ✓ ✓ Made In USA ✓ ✓ ✓ ✓ ✓

title: Vanity Fair Women's Illumination String Bikini Panties, Silky Stretch & Satin Trim
text: From the manufacturer Read more Read more Illumination Bikini Bikinis are low-rise and sit on the hips, with thin sides and a higher cut leg. They help cover up while maintaining a modern style. Bikinis are super versatile and flatter all body types, making them a good option for most easy, breezy outfits. Illumination Hi Cut Hi-Cut panties are a mix between Bikinis and Briefs, providing more coverage than a Bikini at the tummy and back but not quite as much as a Brief. Hi-Cut panties also sit higher up on the thigh which makes your legs look longer. Hi-Cut panties are a perfect partner for high-waisted pants and skirts. Illumination Brief Briefs offer the most all-around coverage. Designed for comfort and fit above all else, they usually sit higher on the waist. They have a simple silhouette and typically come in soft fabrics like cotton, nylon, or microfiber. Briefs are a great no-show option to wear under clothing that skims and glides, like dresses and skirts. Illumination Hipster Hipsters are most like a Bikini, but they offer slightly more coverage with wider sides and lower cut legs. Hipsters also tend to have a low rise, sitting just below the waist which makes them a great option for low-rise jeans and pants. Read more

title: Koral Jewelry Round Moonstone 925 Sterling Silver Ring - Delicate Boho Chic Jewelry - Fashionable and Stylish for Girls and Women with Velvet Bag/Gift Box- Made by Indian Artisans - Size 5-10
text: Product Description KORAL JEWELRY WHERE OUR CUSTOMERS ARE THE JEWELS IN OUR CROWN At Koral Jewelry we make it our business to bring our customers the most stunning adornments. We use only the very best materials of exceptional quality such as the 925 sterling silver and real moonstone gems which are in these rings to ensure that you receive jewelry which you will be proud to wear. At the same time, we make our jewelry affordable. We believe that you should be able to have as much jewelry as you like without compromising on quality and genuine materials. A RING WHICH DRAWS THE EYE TO IT As light enters the gem stone, it is refracted and scattered, producing an extremely unique and attractive play of both color and light which automatically draws the eye to it. You’ll find yourself mesmerized by the stone as it changes in natural daylight and the artificial light of the evening. MINIMALISTIC AND CHARMING That is the way we would describe this piece. It is elegance itself while being still suitable for daywear or evening wear. AN AMAZING GIFT The perfect gift for your favorite lady whether she’s your wife, your mother, your sister, your daughter or your friend. A beautiful graduation gift, Valentine’s Day gift, Mother’s Day, Christmas gift, anniversary, birthday gift and so much more. The ring comes in a beautiful velvet presentation bag. A FEW LITTLE CARE TIPS Keep your silver jewelry looking its best: * Do not wear while cleaning * Do not expose to harsh chemicals * Do not wear in the pool or spa * Store your jewelry individually to prevent scratching * Anti-tarnish strips are perfect to keep the silver looking sparkling clean PLACE IN YOUR CART NOW for yourself or as a gift because we at Koral Jewelry are ALWAYS HERE FOR YOU. text: Product Description Originally designed for heavy use in the corporate environment, this DELL computer has been Renewed with higher quality components than you'll find in typical off-the-shelf retail models. Specifically configured for optimal use at home or school, this computer has been professionally refurbished by a Microsoft Authorized Refurbisher (MAR). Every component is tested for full functionality to ensure years of ongoing performance and reliability. Exterior cosmetics are restored to a like-new condition with little to no visible signs of previous use. A fresh and authentic installation of Microsoft Windows 10 is performed with the new license digitally rendered in the PC for an easy and secure start upon first use. title: Restore (00016 8-Cylinder Formula Engine Restorer & Lubricant - 16 oz.
text: Product Description Restore Engine Restorer & Lubricant is a high performance oil additive that increases compression in older high-mileage engines. The unique CSL formula fills worn areas of the cylinder walls to reduce blow-by and restore compression to near original levels. Restoring cylinder compression improves combustion to increase horsepower, reduce oil burning, maximize fuel mileage and restore peak engine performance. In addition, it provides extreme pressure lubrication to help protect engine components from excessive wear. Compatible with conventional or synthetic oil. title: Kentucky Bluegrass Seed: Blue Ribbon Blend (500 Sq')
text: Product Description Enjoy the benefits of a high quality Kentucky Bluegrass lawn now even faster. With 20% quick-growing perennial ryegrass added to the mix, waiting around for grass to grow in northern States is a thing of the past. There's a reason we call this our 'Blue Ribbon' Kentucky Bluegrass Seed blend. Over twenty years of hands-on experience, research and customer feedback has gone into developing this Seed mix. The result is a premium blend of Elite type Kentucky Bluegrass and perennial ryegrasses designed to provide the highest quality genetic color and texture while reducing the need for constant fertilizing. By using this combination, we take advantage of the unique strengths of both. The ryegrasses grow quickly to establish the lawn, while the slower growing bluegrasses come in later and push out other species to provide the fantastic color and feel to this lawn. Our most popular and requested blend, it's perfect for residential Lawns, sport Turf, heavy traffic areas and areas where children and pets play outside. This Seed blend is designed to perform best in the northern United States, from northern California to Illinois and new York. Great plains region, intermountain West region, mid-west/mid-Atlantic region, Pacific northwest region, south-Atlantic transitional region, Southwest transitional region.
