title: Shantihi Yoga Strap for Stretching – Super Soft Adjustable Poly Cotton Stretch Strap with D-Ring Buckle. Yoga Accessories for Exercise, Pilates, Fitness, Therapy. 8Ft. (Black)
text: Product Description Shantihi's Story Namaste! My name is Joleen and I’m the founder of Shantihi. I’ve been a yoga practitioner and teacher for many years and throughout those years, I have personally felt the benefits of yoga and seen how yoga can change people’s lives by creating a sense of balance and peace, especially for women who are going through traumatic events or difficult challenges. Shantihi means peace in Sanskrit and I created Shantihi because I wanted a brand that reconnects us back to our hearts , and not just a trendy fashion statement. When I practice with any Shantihi product, I draw on the strength and peace that the brand embodies, empowering me to deal with challenging situations, be it physical or emotional. Above all else, my ultimate mission is to empower people, particularly women, to find strength and heal through the practice of yoga. I would love for you to be a part of this movement so grab a Shantihi Yoga Strap in any color and join me and the Shantihi community on a yoga journey of healing and empowerment today! Here's to Finding Peace Within. ॐ The secret to improving flexibility, finding space and stability in your yoga practice ॐ Are you tired of feeling stiff and tight? Do you want more mobility and freedom of movement? You are not alone. Our modern lifestlye have made our hips, shoulders and joints tighter due to our lack of inactivity. So why is flexibility so important? Flexibility creates a wider range of movement, improves your performance in daily activities (reaching to grab something from the back seat of your car), lowers risk of injuries and enables muscles to work effectively. Maintaining flexibility is an important component of overall fitness. Whether you’re a seasoned yogi or a couch potato, we all need to improve our mobility in order to enjoy a better quality of life. If you're serious about improving your health or deepening your yoga practice, then it’s high time you start using a yoga strap. Grab yourself a Shantihi Yoga Strap and join us on a yoga journey of healing and empowerment today! Why People Love The Shantihi Yoga Strap Extend Your Range Saying you’re not flexible enough for yoga is like saying you’re too dirty to take a bath. Let the strap be your extended limb to reach a little further day by day. Experiment Going A Little Further Experiment with poses that have previously eluded you. Learn to get into advanced poses correctly and safely without pulling a muscle or compromising proper alignment. Super Soft Premium Material You are sure to love our super soft yoga strap which provides a non-slip grip without digging into your skin. The thick and sturdy reinforced poly cotton is made to withstand demanding stretches, yet small and light enough for travels. Read more Strong Core, Better Alignment Find stability and strength by using the yoga strap to keep you safe and aligned. Your yoga strap will assist you in holding your pose longer and creating a stable base, especially in arm balances. Great for beginners. Perfect For All Shapes & Sizes The D-ring buckle allows you to adjust the 8 ft yoga strap according to your height, shape of your body and the pose you are attempting. This strap is good for runners, dancers, yogis, pilates practitioners and other athletes. Recommended By Physical Therapists Professionals in the fitness industry have been recommending the use of yoga straps for stretching tight muscles, hips and joints. You can use straps to lift injured and recovering limbs during physical therapy . Read more Go on, add a yoga strap (or two) to cart today! Save more when you buy multiple yoga straps . Click ”Add to Cart” now to start taking your practice and flexibility to a new level in a safe and effective way. This makes a great gift so pick another color for your yogi buddy too! We have them in Black and Cream. Please enjoy your bonus eBook Guide on "Using Your Yoga Strap Effectively" with your purchase. Check out our other products below for more discounts with purchase. Here’s to Finding Peace Within . Namaste, Shantihi Yoga Read more Complete Your Shantihi Yoga Collection Shantihi Eco Yoga Mat (24"x72") Using TPE, the latest technological improvement to the traditional yoga mat. This yoga mat is non-toxic, free from PVC, phthalates, silicone and other harmful chemicals. Get your own and never have to share studio mats again. Search for Shantihi Yoga Mat . Available in Black, Dark Blue and Dark Purple. Shantihi Hot Yoga Towel (24"x72") Are you tired of slipping on your yoga mat, especially when you are trying to hold a pose during sweaty practices? This yoga towel will keep you stable and grounded while feeling cleaner and dryer. Search for Shantihi Yoga Towel. Available in Blue, Gray and Purple. Shantihi Exercise Hand Towel (24"x15") Great complement to your Shanthi Hot Yoga Towel using the same quality material and stitching, only much smaller. It is lightweight, compact and very handy to absorb extra sweat. Search for Shantihi Gym Towel . Available in Blue, Gray and Purple. When you practice with any Shantihi product, you draw on the strength and peace that the brand embodies, empowering you to deal with challenging situations be it physical or emotional. Join our movement of healing and empowerment today! Read more

title: KONG Coolers | 25 Quart Rotomolded | Proudly Made in The USA | Durable, Safe, No-Slip Feet, Extended Ice Retention Cooler
text: Product Description 25 Quart Rotomolded Cooler The KONG 25 is incredibly durable, and it really packs a punch. Perfectly sized for sidekick duty, this cooler holds enough for the bare necessities and then some. CAPACITY The KONG 25 Quart cooler holds up to 18 - 12oz cans and 12.5 pounds of ice! EXTENDED ICE RETENTION 25 QT KONG Coolers are designed to outlast your adventure with up to 5+ day ice retention! DIVIDED STORAGE & ACCESSORIES Our dividers double as a shelf, triple as a cutting board, and quadruple as a side table with the kicker. Use to keep food dry and drinks on ice. Customize your cooler to fit your needs with accessories like the Bottle Biter and Krush Guards. STAY-PUT LID A subtle yet awesome feature that’s unique to KONG Coolers! The lid will open to a 45-degree angle while backed up against a wall or other object. The ability to get into your cooler when you’ve packed your gear tight and you’re thirsty is beyond compare. Read more CAM ACTION LATCHES Made from 3/16-inch-thick, rigid nylon with stainless steel hardware, our latches shut tight to secure your stash and won’t break or rot like rubber. Unlike competitors that put their latches on the lid, our latches move downward in order to stay out of the cooler and allow the lid to close. Over center cam action provides a super tight seal that provides awesome insulation. The latch’s stainless-steel hardware can stand up to even the saltiest of conditions. The beneficial uses of apple cider vinegar have only regained popularity recently and now you can enjoy the noted health benefits of drinking apple cider vinegar without the bitter taste and pungent scent. Apple cider vinegar helps balance the body's pH levels and has numerous health benefits due to the proteins, enzymes, bacteria and acetic acid it contains. By improving healthy bacterial balance, use of apple cider vinegar is a natural way to support skin, digestive, and immune system health. Country Farms Apple Cider Vinegar Dietary Supplement Capsules are formulated to also include the health benefits of ginger, cayenne and maple. title: The Original Magic Wand with Free Wand Essentials Travel Massager, White
text: Product Description Rebranding of the Hitachi Magic Wand: Because of its concerns about having its name attached to a popular massager, Hitachi decided to cease production of the Magic Wand in 2013. Vibratex persuaded Hitachi to continue manufacturing the device, to rename it the "Original Magic Wand", to use lighter, more durable materials, and to omit any reference to Hitachi. The newly named device returned to the market on 25 June 2013, with improved engineering and modified graphic design on its accompanying box. Please know that you are getting an authentic Original Magic Wand. Wand Length: 13.5" Bonus! This kit includes a soft-molded Wand Essential Massager Attachment. Wand Length: 13.5". Now get a bonus WAND ESSENTIALS mini back massager with purchase. title: Kwikset 99160-016 SmartCode 916 Modern Contemporary Touchscreen Smart Lock Deadbolt featuring SmartKey Security and Z-Wave Plus, Satin Nickel
text: Product Description The SmartCode touchscreen smart lock with Home Connect technology enables the lock to wirelessly communicate with other devices in home. The lock allows the user (through a web enabled device) to remotely check the door lock status, lock or unlock the door and receive notifications. SmartCode is a one-touch locking motorized deadbolt. With your personalized code, you can enter your home with the convenience of keyless entry and the back-lit keypad provides increased visibility. It features patented SecureScreen™ technology to prevent code detection from fingerprints on the touchscreen. SmartCode is easy to install, program and use, and operates on 4 AA batteries. It also features SmartKey Security as the back-up keyway. This single cylinder deadbolt can be locked or unlocked by using the keypad or key from the outside as well as the turn button from the inside. The crisp, clean appearance of the Satin Nickel finish adds to the overall look of the product and brings a modern feel. Kwikset smartcode dead bolts are available as smart locks and as electronic deadbolts to provide keyless entry and access for your daily life similar to our Kwikset Kevo door lock. Our Kwikset locks come with patented Kwikset only security features including- Kwikset smartkey security and SecureScreen. Our front door locks are the smart choice whether you are searching for a keypad lock or a touchscreen lock with multiple finishes including satin nickel, venetian bronze, and polished chrome. From august to december Kwikset deadbolts are the locks for year-round keyless entry. Kwikset smartcode home connect means our kwikset z wave locks works with amazon alexa, smartthings, and wink smart home hubs for smart home automation. text: Product Description Life is Getting More and More Stressful and Avonleigh Linens will be your Secret to Relaxing at The End Of A Long Day. Richness and Longevity : - Our 400 Thread Count sheets have been crafted with silky sateen weave using the long-staple cotton fiber, Ultra Soft feathery touch hand feel along with the Richness look and enhances the durability of the sheets. These sheets are manufactured with 100% pure long-staple cotton combed yarn in such a way that it retains softness after wash and fade to resistance. To maintain the softness, we would recommend regular laundering. Also, Available in Full, Full Fitted, Standard / Queen Pillow Pair, Queen, Queen Fitted, King, King Fitted, California King, California King Fitted. Our customers sleep happier - not just comfortably enveloped in soft breathable cotton. Our extra-long staple (ELS) cotton sheets are both luxurious and lasting and are produced in a factory powered entirely by wind and green facility. Classic Comfort with 400 TC Wrinkle Free Sheet Set designs in US-style and made from 100% pure long-staple cotton combed yarn, fabric woven on modern European electronic looms, the best quality process for long-lasting color, brightness. This sheet set may cause you to enter a state of never leaving your bed in the morning due to its extreme softness. Give yourself the gift of a revitalizing night’s sleep with our Egyptian Cotton Sheet Set. Known for its long-lasting durability and comfort. Care Instruction - We recommend washing your sheet on a cool or warm cycle, and line-drying to preserve the fibers, color, and elasticity. If you're using a dryer, choose a low heat and low tumble cycle for the best results. Our Promise avonleigh LINENS provides customers with Richness that they can feel good about. Our promise is simple: we provide a superior product in an accessible way. We feel that our customers deserve ethically made, environmentally sustainable, accessibly-cost home linens without comprising on quality, comfort, or style. Quality you have never experienced before! We use High strength durable stitching threads, premium quality long-lasting Elastic on fitted sheets, and leave optimum pocket depth to fit the standard and deep mattress. Every yard of the fabric we use is inspected at every stage and each sheet set is again individually inspected before being packed and shipped from the factory. By offering impeccable quality controls and versatility, a comfy Sheet will enable you to elevate your sleep experience from ordinary to Extraordinary. Each of our pieces is individually inspected before being packed and shipped. Why We're Different We came to the realization that our industry needed change. We became stewards of change when we began manufacturing a high-quality product in an environmentally and socially responsible way. What kept us up at night then is what helps our clients sleep better now. Our workers are well-treated and well-paid. Our linens are shipped directly from our factory. By cutting out the middlemen, we offer some of the industry’s best products. YOUR TRUST AND OUR SATISFACTION : Night's sleep is something that set's off for a good day, and We believe in "live well, sleep well". To ensure, we test our product and inspect each piece, it to be defect-free, which makes these sheets an ideal gift for any occasion for men and women, Mother’s Day, Father’s Day, Valentine’s Day, and Christmas. These sheets design can match any home décor and would be perfect for any room in your home. So why to wait?

title: Spyderco Endura 4 Lightweight Signature Knife with 3.80" VG-10 Steel Blade and Zome Green FRN Handle - PlainEdge - C10ZFPGR
text: From the brand Previous page Signature Knives Value Folder Knives USA Made Knives Sharpeners Salt Series Knives Specialty Knives Flipper Knives Prestige Knives Fixed Blade Knives Culinary Knives Byrd Knives Next page Product Description Read more Read more Endura 4 Lightweight CRAFTED FOR LIFE If you already own a Delica or Endura, you have one of signature knives Spyderco makes. The knife you have just acquired is a bit different from the normal C10 Endura 4 and C11 Delica 4 Lightweights. They are now available in a range of new handle colors with full-flat ground blades. Their FRN (fiberglass reinforced nylon) handles come in new vibrant tones including blue, green, brown, gray, and purple. Molded onto the handle's surface is Bi-Directional Texturing for slip-free tactile traction. Inside the handle are dual skeletonized stainless steel liners which strengthen the knife without additional weight and double as an anchor for external and internal components to attach through generating more sturdiness and rigidity. The blades are full flat-ground VG-10 with a thinner highly refined cutting edge and a larger 13mm opening hole. Added to the blade's spine is slip resistant jimping. Phosphor bronze washers smooth out the open/close action and the clip is upgraded to a four-way tip-up, tip-down, left-or right-handed clip. title: Jssmst Locking Large Metal Cash Box with Money Tray, Money Box with Combination Lock, Black
text: Product Description Jssmst is a professional safe box manufacturer for more than 24 years and brand owner targeted at US customers. Our main products are mailbox, security safe, gun safe, book safe, cash box, medical box, gun box, and other safe boxes. All series of our products have passed the tests from SGS. High Quality Jssmst Safe Lock Box is built using only the high-grade components, durable materials ensure reliability and safety. 100% Satisfied Free User Support Every purchase includes our lifetime support. If you have any questions, our friendly customer support team will be more than happy to help out. Upgraded Metal Dials With upgraded code design, you wouldn’t have to change your cash box every year. Cover on Coin Trays New Design by adding a cover on coin trays, to hold coins inside the lock box. Four Spring Clips Four strong spring clips help to organize paper bills and checks separately. Sturdy Convenient Handle With sturdy convenient handle, you can carry the box everywhere and hidden it easily. Read more FOUR STEPS TO SET THE PASSWORD Step 1 Keep dials at original password "000" and turn the knob to "unlock" position to open the cash box. Step 2 - Important Use two fingers(thumb and forefinger) to move the lock slot from A to side, then up to B. Don't move it from A to B directly, it will be stuck. Step 3 Set your password, e.g. "111", make sure all numbers are in the center of the dials. Step 4 Be sure to move the slot back to A. Your password is "111'. Read more

title: Q Timex Men's 38mm Watch
text: From the manufacturer Read more Q Timex Our Q Timex Reissue series brings back some of our most iconic designs from the 1970s, a time when the quartz crisis was turning the mechanical watch industry upside down. Rotating Bezel When you align the center mark of your rotating bezel with the current position of the minute hand, you can then read elapsed time on the bezel. Domed Crystal Found in many vintage watches, domed acrylic crystals are shatter resistant making them preferred for dive watches. You’ll see slight dial distortion at extreme angles, an organic curve as the crystal arcs above the case, and a warmth not seen with glass. Old-School Battery Hatch The caseback hatch is a design relic from the 1970s, when watch batteries only lasted months. Some modern batteries last nearly ten years, but we remained true to our archival designs. And you may thank us after a decade of use. Read more Diver-Inspired Design With bold luminescent hands, oversized markers, and an elapsed-time bezel, we kept the integrity of the diver style without the expense of a deep sea helium relief valve. Woven Stainless Steel Bracelet Hundreds of woven stainless steel links give you a durable polished look with a flexible fit. Tested Under Pressure In the 1960s we tested the durability of our watches on boat motors, the wrist of cliff divers and even in dishwashers. And we did it all on live television. Today, nearly every Timex watch is tested for water resistance and accuracy for 24 hours before it leaves our hands. Read more

title: RK Racing Chain 520XSO-108 (520 Series) Steel 108 Link High Performance Street and Off-Road RX-Ring Chain with Connecting Link
text: Product Description The RK Chain factory has made a running production upgrade to their best selling 520XSO chain. The new upgrade GBXSO and non-gold XSO chains features RK's proprietary "RX-Ring" seal design and is offered in 520, 525 and 530. All versions are available in either gold/gold or standard steel color. Viewed in cross-section, the RK "RX-Ring" has two lubrication pools and seal points versus the single seal point/pool design of a regular O-ring chain. RK's new GBXSO chains offer quality, performance and unbeatable value, for all but the most demanding high performance application. title: ESPEEDER Universal 10AN Aluminum Baffled Oil Catch Can Brushed Reservoir Tank with Breather Filter 750ml Black
text: Product Description WHAT IS A CATCH CAN? A catch can is technically an oil/air separator. Catch cans / oil separators are used to separate oil droplets from the air circulating from the engine breather and then through the intake system. that can greatly benefit direct-injected engines. They prevent oil and other contaminants from causing buildup inside your engine's intake manifold. Solve the Problem - Oil Catch Can 1. By installing an oil catch can on your turbo car, it will collect oil and moisture blow by gases from PCV valve or engine Valve Cover ports going to intake system. Keep your engine to perform at its best for the longest period of time; 2. With oil catch can you can keep your engine clean under hard driving conditions allowing "cleaner" gases to be passed back into the intake; 3. The oil catch can will remove carbon and sludge build-up in the intake system, prolong engine longevity, increase engine performance. Application: Filtered Breather that traps oil while allowing air to escape freely, and the baffle system in the oil tank also could filter the air, reduce oil and gas into the intake manifold. Don't use the filter on a PCV system, you'll just break the vacuum and cause engine problems. The filter is for pre-PCV cars. Features: Anodized Body High quality material: Made with High Quality Aluminum for Enhanced Strength and Durability Ensure Better Mileage, Better Performance and Preserve Engine Life Hose Clamp: Prevents oil leakage Built in Dipstick: To Check Fluid Level Removable Bottom to Drain The oil catch tank is universal and fits for most cars Universal for most cars, as long as have enough space. 2 types Of Installation: Easy to install oil catch can with breather filter as a vent system or without breather filter as a seal can, all for your option. title: DirectGlow 16oz UV Blacklight Reactive Fluorescent Acrylic Paints (Red)
text: Product Description This is that hard to find premium blend acrylic based blacklight paint. Do not confuse this product with other cheap novelty type fluorescent paints. Acrylic blend paints dry to a smooth hard finish and will not simply wash off with a little bit of water like other brands. The colors are highly fluorescent in normal lighting and really pop out under blacklighted conditions! Specially formulated by DirectGlow, these paints will add bright and vibrant colors to your special project. There are no harsh chemicals and is completely safe for general use. The finish can be protected with a water based sealant for long lasting effects. Great for arts and crafts, safety marking, glow parties, theatrical effects, fishing lures, and anything else you can think of. Available in numerous other sizes and colors in our store. Lower price for higher volume! Formulated and manufactured by DirectGlow exclusively. PLEASE NOTE UV RED IS A NEON RED. DARKER REDS DO NOT POP IN BLACKLIGHT. THE RED WILL BE A VERY BRIGHT NEON RED. text: From the brand Previous page Contemplated in 1972, Jay "Sparky" Longley tested making sandals in his Laguna Beach garage. With 200 dollars, he bought a sewing machine, some rubber & started his goal: To make the best sandal. He officially began Rainbow Sandals, Inc in 1974. Today, we make 2 million pairs a year. Our goal has always been to make a quality product that will not end up as landfill and that goal does not end when our sandals leave the store. 48 years later, our Rainbow Sandals Factory Outlet is still located at 326 Calle de Los Molinos, San Clemente, CA. All our customers say, 'I love my Rainbow Sandals,' and I hope you will too." - Jay R Longley, Jr. We love hearing the stories people write us about the countless miles they have walked in our sandals. title: Eau Thermale Avene RICH Revitalizing Nourishing Cream, Ultra Nourishing Face Moisturizer, Non-comedogenic 1.6 fl. oz.
text: From the manufacturer Daily Essential Care Upgrade your daily skincare routine with ultra-nourishing, glow-boosting essentials. Stress, Burnout & Fatigue Not Only Take a Toll on the Mind & Body, But Also Shows on the Skin Too Stress and lack of sleep can cause increased Cortisol levels, which makes the body retain fat & restrict blood flow - affecting the production of collagen. Ultimately accelerating the aging process and effecting skin's ability to repair itself. The signs? Large pores, persistent dryness and dullness. Avène's new solution, Les Essentiels, for dull, fatigued skin revitalizes that energetic glowing complexion. Revitalize Dull, Fatigued Skin A Nourishing Complex to Restore Radiant, Illuminated Complexion Natural Red Fruit Extract, a combination of raspberries, blueberries and redcurrants instantly supply skin with lipids to strengthen and restore healthy skin barrier. Pre-Tocopheryl, patented Vitamin E, time released antioxidant protection provides a free radical shield. Avène Thermal Spring Water clinically shown by 150 studies to soothe, soften and calm. Find the Signs of Skin Fatigue Puffy Eyes Tired skin retains water near the eyes to stay hydrated, making them look puffy. Use a cream to help decongest the eye contour. Persistent Dryness Fine, dehydration lines and dull, dry skin can appear with lack of sleep. Use a rich nourishing cream to nourish, restore a radiant, luminescent glow. Dull, Lackluster Skin When skin barrier is healthy, it retains moisture & nutrients better. Supply skin with nourishing lipids to help keep skin barrier strong and healthy. Enlarged Pores Skin needs to regenerate while you sleep so be sure to cleanse dirt, oil and pollutants that can stick to make-up through the day & clog pores. The Company Behind the Brand The Pierre Fabre Botanical Expertise Eau Thermale Avène founder, Pierre Fabre, was a passionate pharmacist, botanist, entrepreneur & humanitarian that focused his business on three pillars: dermo-cosmetics & health care products. Pierre Fabre botanical expertise is a continuous improvement approach that helps responsibly develop plant-based, innovative, safe and effective ingredients. This is done through sustainable selection of plant extraction methods that respect Humankind and nature. About Eau Thermale Avene

Pre-Tocopheryl, patented Vitamin E, time released antioxidant protection provides a free radical shield. Avène Thermal Spring Water clinically shown by 150 studies to soothe, soften and calm. Find the Signs of Skin Fatigue Puffy Eyes Tired skin retains water near the eyes to stay hydrated, making them look puffy. Use a cream to help decongest the eye contour. Persistent Dryness Fine, dehydration lines and dull, dry skin can appear with lack of sleep. Use a rich nourishing cream to nourish, restore a radiant, luminescent glow. Dull, Lackluster Skin When skin barrier is healthy, it retains moisture & nutrients better. Supply skin with nourishing lipids to help keep skin barrier strong and healthy. Enlarged Pores Skin needs to regenerate while you sleep so be sure to cleanse dirt, oil and pollutants that can stick to make-up through the day & clog pores. The Company Behind the Brand The Pierre Fabre Botanical Expertise Eau Thermale Avène founder, Pierre Fabre, was a passionate pharmacist, botanist, entrepreneur & humanitarian that focused his business on three pillars: dermo-cosmetics & health care products. Pierre Fabre botanical expertise is a continuous improvement approach that helps responsibly develop plant-based, innovative, safe and effective ingredients. This is done through sustainable selection of plant extraction methods that respect Humankind and nature. About Eau Thermale Avene

title: TAYLOR MADE PRODUCTS Square Low Freeboard Fender for Fishing Boats Metallic Black, 5" x 14"
text: Product Description Protect your low freeboard boat with a fender you can trust. The patented design of the Taylor Made® Low Freeboard Fender gives your boat protection like never before. Its unique, square shape keeps this fender from rolling out of place — helping to better protect the gunwales and rub rail of low freeboard boats. Constructed from heavy-duty, marine grade vinyl, our fenders are built to take on rigors of life on the water. Plus, it comes equipped with a rubber football needle valve for easy inflation and extended longevity. And like all of our fenders, the Low Freeboard Fender is crafted right here in the USA by a name boat owners know and trust. No Compromising. The Brand Boaters Trust. Unrivaled quality. From the first custom canvas piece created in 1908 by Nelson Taylor, Taylor Made has been setting the standard for design and product excellence in boat fenders, buoys, dock products, and a wide variety of other boating accessories. Boaters everywhere trust the Taylor Made brand to deliver top-performing, high-quality products for their marine needs. Taylor Made is a proud member of Lippert, a leading, global manufacturer and supplier of highly engineered products and customized solutions dedicated to shaping, growing, and bettering the RV, marine, automotive, commercial vehicle, and building products industries. Whether you're on the road or the water, our team is always thinking about your next journey, pushing the possibilities of our products, all to better your time spent outdoors, whenever, wherever, for years to come. Boat Fenders Fenders Taylor Made knows fenders. For more than 60 years, Taylor Made has been protecting boats of all sizes. Boaters rely on innovative engineering and superior design in every fender made, whether for a yacht or personal watercraft and everything in-between. Fender Covers Fenders protect your boat, but what protects your fenders? Our fender covers not only provide maximum protection to your boat without scuffing or marring the gelcoat they also extend the life of your fenders. Fender Adjusters Boaters need to quickly and easily adjust their boat fenders when approaching unfamiliar docks, rafting, and mooring. Taylor Made has designed a range of fender adjusters to take the worry out of dealing with awkward knots and effortlessly adjusting fenders to the exact height needed. Read more Buoys Marker Buoys Taylor Made marker buoys help identify safety areas, guide boats into channels, mark water ski courses, and a great fishing spot. Our marker buoys come in highly visible colors and can take on heavy-duty applications and the rigors of a marine environment. Mooring Buoys Built tough with a hard, polyethylene skin, our mooring buoys have ultra-violet light absorbers for long-term life in the sun. The blue reflective stripe offers high visibility day or night. Many buoys have a tube-through-the-center design allowing your anchor chain easy pass-through for mooring applications. Buoy Accessories Taylor Made boat buoy accessories help your buoys perform when and where you need them the most. From mooring collars to replacement hardware, these accessories are tough and durable. They are designed to work with Taylor Made buoys as well as other buoys with the center tube design. Read more Dock Accessories Dock Boxes Boaters need a convenient, dry and safe place to store life jackets, cushions, fishing gear and more. Taylor Made fiberglass dock boxes are coated with a durable UV gelcoat finish with a solid foam core that contains no trapped air, making it more resistant to water and odors. Gas shocks are standard with our fiberglass boxes that keep the lid open in high winds and are easy to close. Dock Carts Taylor Made has designed a reliable way for boaters to get their gear from their vehicle to their vessel with their dock carts and designed with an easy-to-use handle that minimizes leaning when transporting from one spot to another. The angled-up tub allows for more leg clearance and no bumping into your shins. These carts are versatile and can be used for marine and other applications such as gardening or lawn work. Dock Steps Getting on and off your boat should not be a challenge. Taylor Made dock steps have a non-slip pad for maximum protection for a secure and safe entry and exit to any vessel in dry or wet conditions. These dock steps are available in single, double and triple treads and are easily mounted to any dock. Read more Dock Protection Dock Wheels Taylor Made dock wheels are a great protector and offer substantial dock cushioning. They have a molded-in inflation valve that is available in corners and straight mounts to adjust the specific level of firmness you need. Our dock wheels come with heavy-duty hot-dipped galvanized hardware for easy installation. Dock Edging Taylor Made has a wide variety of dock edging applications that protect your boat from taking on any damage from contact with sharp edges and corner of docks, piers or floats. EPDM rubber and commercial-grade vinyl dock edging are easy to install and tolerate harsh UV-rays and the marine environment. Piling Caps Protecting dock pilings from water damage or bird nests can be prevented with Taylor Made piling caps. These dock caps are made with strong polypropylene that will protect your dock or pier pilings. These piling caps give your dock a more finished look. Read more

title: SUPERIOR Indoor 2' x 3' Area Rug with Jute Backing, Unique Decor for Kitchen, Bedroom, Living-Dining Room, Entryway, Hallway, Perfect for Hardwood Floors - Viking Modern Trellis Design, Chocolate
text: Product Description Incorporate a welcoming yet dramatic look to your interiors with the beautifully designed Viking Indoor Area Rug. The versatile Moroccan trellis design creates a fascinating display of stylish opulence that will coordinate effortlessly with your surrounding décor. The 100-percent Polypropylene base and well-made jute backing are sturdy enough for even the most heavily frequented areas of your home. Viking boasts a 0.39-inch rug thickness (10mm) to create a soft feeling underfoot that is ideal for everyday use. This product meets the required criteria to be OEKO-TEX certified. OEKO-TEX textiles and fabrics are tested and verified to be free of harmful chemicals and substances. SUPERIOR VIKING CONTEMPORARY GEOMETRIC TRELLIS INDOOR AREA RUG Add a dramatic accent to your tile or hardwood floors with this modern-inspired area rug. The modern and sleek geometric trellis pattern will highlight your tile or hardwood floors while coordinating effortlessly with any contemporary or transitional interior. 0.31” rug thickness is easy to maintain, allows chairs sitting atop this rug to slide easily, and is sure to clear any doorway in your home. Sturdy power-loomed construction. OEKO-TEX certified. Fabrics and textiles that meet OEKO-TEX standards are free of harmful chemicals and substances. Read more Cultivating Mix of Texture and Color PRETTY AND PRACTICAL The warm and earthy palette of the large-scale trellis pattern makes an opulent yet bold statement to any room in your home. EASY YET TAILORED STYLE Crafted from Polypropylene with a long-lasting jute backing, this family-friendly rug is durable enough to handle your most frequented indoor areas of your home. HARDWORKING AND VERSATILE The sturdy power-loomed construction is made with everyday durability to handle your most frequented indoor areas such as kitchens, family rooms, basements, and entryways. CREATE A COZY FOUNDATION Ideal for homes with children and pets, this rug can resist common spills and stains making it perfect for everyday use. Pro tip: Runners are the perfect way to dress up any hallway in your home or decorate any narrow space that could use a cozier foundation. Small Scatter Rug Size: 2' x 3' and 3' x 5' Recommended Room: Entryway, Kitchen, Bathroom, Laundry Room, Playroom Pro tip: This versatile rectangular size works great in front of doorways and can also work as a small landing space when you need a little extra padding. Medium Rug Size: 4' x 6', 5’ Round, 5’ x 5’, 5' x 8', 6' x 9' and 7’ x 9’ Recommended Room: Living Room, Bedroom, Playroom, Dining Room Pro tip: Perfect for smaller living spaces, it's easy to define a specific seating area with a medium-size rug. Large Area Rugs: 8’ Round, 8’ x 8’, 8' x 10' and 9' x 12' Recommended Room: Bedroom, Living Room, Dining Rooms, Nursery Pro tip: Create a central focus to any medium or large living area that provides a soft cushion underfoot while also framing your space.

title: Arteck HB192 Universal Bluetooth Keyboard Multi-Device Stainless Steel Full Size Wireless Keyboard for Windows iOS Android Computer Desktop Laptop Surface Tablet Smartphone Rechargeable Battery
text: Product Description Industry Leading Ergonomic Design Stainless steel material gives heavy duty feeling and the low-profile keys offer quiet and comfortable typing. It allows you to gain quick access to common functions, such as volume level, playback control, copy paste text, and more. It also provides arrow keys, number pad with slim and compact design. Switch Between 3 Devices with A Single Clicking This keyboard is able to connect to 3 devices at the same time. After you pair the keyboard with 3 devices by long pressing the blue key at the first time, you can simply switch the keyboard to type on any of the device with a single key clicking. Cross Platform Compatible Fully functional to all four major operating system: IOS / Android / MacOS / Windows, and features system-specific function keys for each operating systems. Any Bluetooth supported devices such as laptop, computer, tablet, smartphone can easily be paired and gained quick access to common functions, such as volume level, playback control, copy paste text, and more. Comfortable, quiet typing The whisper-quiet, low-profile keys bring a whole new level of comfort to your fingertips. What's more, keep all your most-used functions and media controls closer than ever Windows-dedicated hot keys. Keyboard with scissors kick construction can be used more than 3 million times continuously. Rechargeable Battery Built-in industry-high rechargeable Li-polymer battery provides 6-month use on a single charge. (based on 2 hours non-stop use per day) 2 Years Warranty If you have problem to use the keyboard, you can reconnect the keyboard and the keyboard has 3 channels to change. If you still have the issue, you can contact the support team printed at the back of the keyboard as the product has 2 years warranty. title: Create Share Play Imagine Dream Vinyl Lettering Wall Decal Sticker (4"H x 47"L, Black)
text: Product Description Vinyl decals are are a quick, fun, and easy way to add to your home décor! They are much easier, cheaper, cleaner, and quicker than stencils or paint and look better too! Our wall decals are made in the USA from high quality self-adhesive vinyl. Your design is computer cut exactly like you see it in the picture. They are easy to install, last for years, and are completely removable when you are ready. Vinyl decals are removable, but typically not reusable. Vinyl decals can be used on numerous surfaces, including but not limited to: walls, mirrors, glass, metal, wood, plastic, paper, ceramic, and many more! Decals are perfect for crafts, making almost any project easy for all. There are endless fun and creative ways to use vinyl! -DISCLAIMER- Images displayed are for reference only and may not reflect exact size. Please review the measurements posted in the description to help choose the size best for your space. Every monitor has different color settings, so the colors may be slightly different than they appear on your screen. title: Kingole Flannel Fleece Luxury Throw Blanket, Cream White Travel/Throw Size Jacquard Weave Pattern Cozy Couch/Bed Super Soft and Warm Plush Microfiber 350GSM (50 x 60 inches)
text: Product Description We were tired of settling between style and comfort every time we went shopping for a new blanket which is why we decided that it time that the people got what they wanted. We at Kingole set out on a mission to bring our customer fabulous and comfortable throw blankets that offer just the right balance of luxurious softness and jaw-dropping beauty that would make them the target of everyone’s envy. Our fleece throw blanket is ideal for anyone that wants a stylish and classy blanket to keep them warm while they take a nap, relax on their sofa or even when going on a road trip. Simply snuggle up to this fleece throw blanket to enjoy comfort and warmth throughout the year. Comfort You’ll Love To help you enjoy your downtime even more, we made this flannel fleece throw blanket that’s not just soft but lightweight and breathable as well. It’s soft on the skin and doesn’t tie you down thanks to how light it is while being softer than most cotton throws you’ll touch. It’s perfect for indoor and outdoor use in cold weather to help you stay warm without overwhelming you with heat. Snuggle up to the throw blanket for the most comfortable afternoon nap you’ll have all winter on your bed or couch. The 350GSM of microfiber polyester we use is carefully selected to offer reliable and long term use without losing any of its softness. It can withstand wash after wash while maintaining its luxurious softness for repeated use year after year. Jacquard Weave Pattern We use a time consuming and labor intensive Jacquard Weaving process that results in a more stable, stretchable and flexible throw blanket that’s both gentle on the skin and breathable to create a truly luxurious combination of style and comfort. Confidence in Textiles All of our blankets are tested by TESTEX AG, SWISS Textile Testing Institute, Zurich, Switzerland Our products achieve Standard 100 by OEKO-TEX, Confidence in Textiles (SH025 171642.2) Test Report No. SH025.171642.2 Certificate No. SH025 156888 Easy To Maintain Our flannel throw blanket is easy to clean and maintain. It gets softer with each wash to provide long term use. To clean, simply wash separately in cold water and Tumble dry on the lowest setting. Avoid direct heat and bleach. Non-Pilling & Anti-Static You can confidently wash this solid color blanket without worrying about pilling or ruining the gorgeous design. It’s non-pilling and anti-static making the right choice for you and even your pets. Read more Make Your Home Look Good When it comes to the softness of our throw blankets, we make no exceptions but that doesn’t mean we hold back on the looks. Our blankets are carefully designed with a simple yet elegant pattern that effortlessly raises the appeal of your décor simply by just lying around. Thanks to the solid colors of our Jacquard Weave Pattern blankets, you can easily coordinate these with your existing bed sheets or couches to create a truly eye-catching and stylish look for your living room, bedroom or lounge. Unlike the rest, you don’t have to worry about the colors fading even after multiple washes. Different Styles of Blankets Solid Color Blanket 350GSM Made using super soft fabric and offers just the right balance of softness and weight to make sure you stay warm and comfy in every season. It’s breathable making it ideal for warmer seasons and available in multiple different colors. Solid Color With Grid Pattern 350GSM Offers the same comfort and warmth as our solid color blankets but also features a stylish and fashion forward design with grid patterns that makes it a great choice for anyone that wants to spice up the look of their décor. Jacquard Weave Blankets 350GSM Made using a unique jacquard weave technique, this throw blanket offers more durability while being soft and breathable. It features a beautiful design making it a great choice for anyone that wants to be more innovative with the look of their homes décor. Sherpa Fleece Blanket 580GSM Double-Layer This luxurious Sherpa Fleece Blanket is double layered for extra warmth and uses a stylish trim on the edges that gives it a luxurious and fabulous look. It combines Sherpa and flannel fabric to offer unrivaled softness to ensure you stay warm and cozy even on the coldest of nights. title: QSY Home Wrap Around Elastic Eyelet Bed Skirts 14 1/2 Inches Drop Dust Ruffle Three Fabric Sides Easy On/Easy Off Adjustable Polyester Cotton 14 1/2 Inches Drop(Pink Queen/King)
text: Product Description ABOUT BRAND: QSY Home is a registered trademark in US. We focus on the production and sale of household goods. ABOUT PRODUCT: 75% polyester 25% cotton woven fabric bed skirt. Durable high quality fabric. Elegant and soft in simple, solid color design. No platform. Easy fit elastic wrap around bed skirt. Adjustable elastic trimmed ruffle makes it so easy to put on and take off. No need to lift the mattress. CARE INSTRUCTIONS: Machine wash in cold water. Use mild laundry detergent and wash separately. Non-Chlorine bleach when needed. Gentle cycle. Do not iron. Tumble dry no Heat. EASY INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS: Simply place elastic band around bed without moving the box spring or mattress, our bed ruffle smartly designed with new adjustable band with button and buttonhole. Over time, the elastic band may lose elasticity, you can simple make the bed ruffle tighter by using the button on the band, tighten the elastic band by inserting the button into one of the perforations, creating a smaller length elastic band. title: Biscaynebay Textured Fabric Round Tablecloths 60 Inches in Diameter, Burgundy Water Resistant Tablecloths for Dining, Kitchen, Wedding, Parties etc. Machine Washable
text: Product Description Be it a festive family feast for the holidays, an upscale dinner party with your foodie friends, or just weekend morning brunch, your tablescape should always be shining. Biscaynebay tablecloth is crafted from high quality thick and durable polyester fabric which looks luxurious on your tables, complements any dinnerware and works in both traditional and modern settings. Biscaynebay Fabric table cloth , Water Resistant Spill Proof Size specification ROUND 60 inch / 70 inch / 90 inch 108 inch / 120 inch RECTANGLE 52x70 inch / 60x84 inch / 60x108inch 70x108 inch / 70x120 inch 90x132 inch / 90 x 156 inch SQUARE 54x54 inch / 60x60 inch 70x70 inch / 90x90 inch FEATURE Multiple sizes and rich vibrant colors available. Classic plain design, easily pairs with different home styles. Suitable for buffet dinners, dining table, tea table, party, birthday, cafes, banquet, picnic, BBQ, camping, barbecue, indoor, outdoor and everyday use. Read more How to choose a round tablecloth Step 1: Measure the diameter of your table. A diameter is the straight line going through the center of your table . Step 2: You need to know your desired drop length. This depends on the type of event you're planning. And add twice drops to the diameter. For example, the diameter of your table is 48 inch, and you want a 11 inch drop, then add 22 inch to 48 inch, to get 70 inch. The resulting values are the dimensions of the tablecloth you should aim to purchase. How to put on a corset by yourself? 1. Loosen the corset by undoing the centre loops and pulling the back of corset apart 6-7" but don't undo the laces at the bottom of the corset. 2. Carefully line up the two sides of your busk on the front of the corset. Line up the pins and the holes and clip the busk together. 3. Tighten the lacing. Starting from the top. Next, go to the bottom of the lacing and pull the laces tighter there. Then working the bottom half of the lacing tighter. 4. Tie off the loose lacing on the back of your corset. text: Product Description The Salt Flag Jacket is made for versatile use on the water. Designed with the classic Helly Hansen flag stripe originating from the Helly Hansen Jackets used by the first Norwegian Whitbread entry the Berge Viking. The Iconic stripe is a classic Marine signoff and with the jacket built in sturdy HellyTech Performance 2 ply fabrication this jackets has what it takes to keep you dry and warm. Packed with right features as a high protective collar and stealth seals in the cuffs the jacket offers top functionality while allowing you to take to the fjords in style. For all situations and weather conditions where protection from the elements is needed. HELLY TECH PERFORMANCE: Highly waterproof and extra breathable sport specific designs and constructions. For a wide range of high performance outdoor activities during highly challenging, changing and unpredictable weather conditions. HELLY TECH PROFESSIONAL: Extremely waterproof and breathable designs and constructions. For highly aerobic, extremely wet or unusually long-lasting activities in extremely harsh conditions. title: InCharacter Bavarian Guy Adult Costume
text: Product Description Includes lederhosen, pullover shirt with lace-up collar, hat and knee socks Product Description Includes lederhosen, pullover shirt with lace-up collar, hat and knee socksFrom the manufacturer About us Our story begins in 1959. Sam Rosenberg wanted to have his own successful business before he retired. Earlier in his adulthood he experienced a few failed start ups. Those were followed by big success as a traveling Salesmen of general merchandise in the 1950s. At the young age of 59, he began the S. Rosenberg Christmas Co . He imported Christmas and Easter novelties and dolls from Japan. In April 1963, Stanley Geller bought the business from his father- in -law, with revenue of approx. He traveled to Japan by propeller planes on buying trips and developed strong relationships with factories there , and sold goods by traveling the roads of the USA in a station wagon filled with samples, going from Minneapolis to Miami, Boston to Bentonville, New York to New Orleans and everywhere in between. Life was tough but good, and the business grew and grew with the help of many people. Read more

title: Noctua NH-L9i, Premium Low-Profile CPU Cooler for Intel LGA115x (Brown)
text: Product Description The NH-L9i is a premium quality quiet CPU cooler for Intel LGA115x/1200 based HTPCs and Small Form Factor systems. At a super-low profile of only 37mm, the NH-L9i is ideal for extremely slim cases and due to its 95x95mm footprint, it provides full compatibility with tall RAM modules and VGA cards on mini-ITX mainboards. The custom designed SecuFirm2 mounting system for LGA115x/1200 makes installation a child’s play and thanks to the highly optimised NF-A9x14 premium fan that supports fully automatic speed control via PWM, the NH-L9i runs remarkably quiet. Topped off with Noctua’s renowned NT-H1 thermal compound, the NH-L9i fuses everything users have come to expect from Noctua’s larger coolers into a super-compact package for slim HTPC systems. 37mm low profile Due to the slim 23mm heatsink and the NF-A9x14 low profile fan that measures only 14mm in thickness, the NH-L9 stands a mere 37mm tall, which makes it ideal for use in compact HTPCs or Small Form Factor cases that offer minimum clearance for CPU coolers. 100% RAM compatibility The NH-L9i has a 95x95mm footprint that complies exactly with the Intel LGA115x/1200 socket keep-out zone. This means that it won't cause issues with chipset coolers and doesn't overhang the RAM slots, so it's fully compatible with tall memory modules. 100% compatibility with PCIe cards on mini-ITX Most Intel LGA115x/1200 based mini-ITX motherboards have the PCIe slot sitting right next to the 95x95mm socket zone. While larger coolers that exceed this zone are likely to block the PCIe slot, the 95x95xmm sized NH-L9i provides full compatibility with PCIe cards. NF-A9x14 PWM premium fan The highly optimised NF-A9x14 premium fan features Noctua's proprietary AAO frame as well as sophisticated aerodynamic design measures. Supporting PWM for fully automatic speed control, the NF-A9x14 allows the NH-L9i to stay remarkably quiet. This treatment also has the added benefit of not affecting your spas pH level, which allows you worry-free application. title: OTC Tools 7402 Universal Outside Thread Chaser
text: Product Description Product Description OTC's Universal Outside Thread Chaser will quickly restore threads on all kinds of objects to near original condition without the use of expensive thread-cutting equipment. The wide variety of cutting heads work on items as varied as faucet heads, threaded containers, fork tubes, steering stems, and much more. Can be used on items varying from 1-1/4 inches O.D. to 5 inches O.D. Designed to be serviced with replaceable cutting heads and v-pad. Durable steel and aluminum construction ensures a long service life and high performance. Kit features 6 die heads with multiple thread sizes per head: 4, 5, 6, 7, 7-1/2, 8, 9, 10, 11, 11-1/2, 12, 14, 16, 18, 20, and 24 threads per inch. Value is at the core of the OTC tool and equipment portfolio. Whether it’s a simple repair or the most complex drivability concern, these award-winning tools universally solve problems faster, and at better value, than any other product line available. Whether it’s a specialty tool or unique piece of service equipment, OTC provides top solutions to modern automotive service challenges while increasing technicians’ productivity and shop profits. title: FIFA 18 Standard Edition - PlayStation 4
text: Product Description Powered by Frostbite, EA SPORTS FIFA 18 blurs the line between the virtual and real worlds, bringing to life the players, teams, and aospheres that immerse you in the emotion of The World’s Game. The biggest step in gameplay innovation in franchise history, FIFA 18 introduces Real Player Motion Technology , an all new animation system which unlocks a new level of responsiveness, and player personality – now Cristiano Ronaldo and other top players feel and move exactly like they do on the real pitch. Player Control combined with new Team Styles and Positioning give you the tools to deliver Dramatic Moments that ignite Immersive Aospheres around the world. The World’s Game also takes you on a global journey as Alex Hunter Returns along with a star studded cast of characters, including Cristiano Ronaldo and other European football stars. GAMEPLAY AND PRESENTATION Powered by Frostbite Attention to innovation in true to life action, new football worlds and character depth, Frostbite helps to further blur the lines between the virtual and real worlds. Using movie studio style advanced shadowing and occlusion techniques to benefit character rendering and overall pitch presentation, FIFA 18 delivers the most visually arresting and authentic football simulation ever. Player Control Real Player Motion Technology: The all new, game changing animation system utilizes pose trajectory matching on every frame to deliver the franchise’s most responsive and fluid gameplay ever. New motion capture techniques and frame by frame animation transitions ensure gameplay accurately represents the reality of football. Real Player Motion Tech is the catalyst for an increased fidelity in movement for every player on the pitch, immediately taking authenticity to another level. Player Personality: Six new character archetypes and new player mapping technology differentiate players on the pitch to give them their own distinct identity. For the first time ever, real world movements, size and attributes inform how a player moves, allowing you to feel the life like tendencies of the world’s best. Ronaldo’s signature sprint, Sterling’s unique turns, and Robben’s distinct arm movement are all immediately recognizable in FIFA 18. Dribbling Overhaul: In FIFA 18, you will run at defenders with confidence knowing that the best players can change direction on a dime. New dribbling mechanics enable players to inject more creativity into 1v1 situations. Take more defined touches, make tighter turns, and explode into attack more dynamically than ever before. Responsive: Creative on ball skills, contextual touches, and a re imagining of the control dribble mechanic give players new options when building up attacks in tight spaces. Change direction with ease and feel your player respond when you escape a defender lunging to tackle. Explosive: Authentic and dynamic speed based animations allow you to explode more rapidly from controlled touches into full tilt sprints. Team Styles and Positioning New Player Positioning: With more freedom in motion, your teammates examine the pitch and react accordingly; darting forward in coordinated runs, or moving into space to provide consistent attacking support. New player positioning gives you a well balanced and spread pitch with more opportunities in time and space to read the play. Team Styles: A deep set of authentic playing styles attributed to several teams put the most recognized tactics on the pitch in FIFA 18 now in AI you will immediately recognize the tiki taka of some of Europe’s best clubs or the high pressing style of teams in the Premier League. Feel a change in defensive and attacking approaches every time you choose a new club or opponent. Dynamic Quick Substitutes: All new context based substitution prompts allow players to easily make changes without pausing the match. Whether it's a missed chance, or necessary response to conceding a goal, you can instantly decide if a change is needed without visiting the menu. Immersive Aospheres Regional Aospheres: Authentic sun positions, cinematic aosphere grading, signature pitch side fixtures, authentic broadcast overlays in La Liga and MLS, on pitch debris, club and stadium specific banners, adaptive commentary, and changes in pitch quality all come together to bring the most immersive football experiences to life in FIFA 18. High Def Dynamic Crowds: All new individual crowd reactions and expanded regional chant support have you feeding off the energy of your supporters. Hear authentic chants build as you mount an attack, incite realistic excitement when you score and even interact with the crowd while celebrating. Dramatic Moments Wonder Goals: New locomotion and finishing animations unlock more fluid striking and heading, combining to increase the potential for more dramatic finishes. Player Personality ensures the heroes of the game stand tall in the biggest moments, finishing more often on the biggest stages. New Crossing Control: All new crossing controls provide the player with a variety of options to put the ball into the box, creating dynamic attacking chances. Whipped to the spot, arching, and back stick crosses increase the variety of delivery to accurately pick out the attacking player. THE JOURNEY: HUNTER RETURNS The World’s Game takes you on a global journey as Alex Hunter returns along with a star studded cast of characters and top football talent, like Ronaldo and other European stars. After a breathtaking first season in the Premier League, Hunter is gaining recognition from top clubs the world over and he is willing to explore any options coming his way. He feels ready to take the next step, his future is bright, and the world is talking about Hunter….but life in football isn’t always fair. Tour the Football World: From a summer break in Brazil, to a pre season tour in Los Angeles, Alex Hunter experiences diverse football landscapes in a truly global journey. More to Play For: Chapter based, short term objectives give Alex Hunter more to play for as he navigates his way through the second season of a prospering career. A Star Studded Cast: Cristiano Ronaldo leads a list of footballing greats and new, diverse characters in a star studded cast well suited to a blockbuster sequel. Impactful Decisions: Players will be faced with bigger and more difficult choices that will alter the story with long term consequences. Shape The Journey narrative in a personal way by making decisions that dictate Alex Hunter's career and effect relationships with characters both on and off the pitch. Your Alex Hunter: Personalize the look of Alex Hunter by selecting his hair, tattoos, and clothing from a series of options. You can even pick Alex's dominant foot to make sure he suits your playing style. Local Multiplayer: Play The Journey as a team through local multiplayer, and experience on pitch action with friends. New Playable Characters: Now players have the option to experience short, standalone stories with new playable characters that Alex meets throughout The Journey. He feels ready to take the next step, his future is bright, and the world is talking about Hunter….but life in football isn’t always fair. Tour the Football World: From a summer break in Brazil, to a pre season tour in Los Angeles, Alex Hunter experiences diverse football landscapes in a truly global journey. More to Play For: Chapter based, short term objectives give Alex Hunter more to play for as he navigates his way through the second season of a prospering career. A Star Studded Cast: Cristiano Ronaldo leads a list of footballing greats and new, diverse characters in a star studded cast well suited to a blockbuster sequel. Impactful Decisions: Players will be faced with bigger and more difficult choices that will alter the story with long term consequences. Shape The Journey narrative in a personal way by making decisions that dictate Alex Hunter's career and effect relationships with characters both on and off the pitch. Your Alex Hunter: Personalize the look of Alex Hunter by selecting his hair, tattoos, and clothing from a series of options. You can even pick Alex's dominant foot to make sure he suits your playing style. Local Multiplayer: Play The Journey as a team through local multiplayer, and experience on pitch action with friends. New Playable Characters: Now players have the option to experience short, standalone stories with new playable characters that Alex meets throughout The Journey.From the manufacturer EA Sports FIFA 18 FIFA 18 you'll experience authentic World Cup gameplay, teams, stadiums, and more. Play through the official tournament structure, craft your own custom tournament using any licensed teams in FIFA 18, or even build your own international dream squad in a FIFA Ultimate Team World Cup. title_text: FIFA 18 Standard Edition - PlayStation 4 / Product Description Powered by Frostbite, EA SPORTS FIFA 18 blurs the line between the virtual and real worlds, bringing to life the players, teams, and aospheres that immerse you in the emotion of The World’s Game. The biggest step in gameplay innovation in franchise history, FIFA 18 introduces Real Player Motion Technology , an all new animation system which unlocks a new level of responsiveness, and player personality – now Cristiano Ronaldo and other top players feel and move exactly like they do on the real pitch. Player Control combined with new Team Styles and Positioning give you the tools to deliver Dramatic Moments that ignite Immersive Aospheres around the world. The World’s Game also takes you on a global journey as Alex Hunter Returns along with a star studded cast of characters, including Cristiano Ronaldo and other European football stars. GAMEPLAY AND PRESENTATION Powered by Frostbite Attention to innovation in true to life action, new football worlds and character depth, Frostbite helps to further blur the lines between the virtual and real worlds. Using movie studio style advanced shadowing and occlusion techniques to benefit character rendering and overall pitch presentation, FIFA 18 delivers the most visually arresting and authentic football simulation ever. Player Control Real Player Motion Technology: The all new, game changing animation system utilizes pose trajectory matching on every frame to deliver the franchise’s most responsive and fluid gameplay ever. New motion capture techniques and frame by frame animation transitions ensure gameplay accurately represents the reality of football. Real Player Motion Tech is the catalyst for an increased fidelity in movement for every player on the pitch, immediately taking authenticity to another level. Player Personality: Six new character archetypes and new player mapping technology differentiate players on the pitch to give them their own distinct identity. For the first time ever, real world movements, size and attributes inform how a player moves, allowing you to feel the life like tendencies of the world’s best. Ronaldo’s signature sprint, Sterling’s unique turns, and Robben’s distinct arm movement are all immediately recognizable in FIFA 18. Dribbling Overhaul: In FIFA 18, you will run at defenders with confidence knowing that the best players can change direction on a dime. New dribbling mechanics enable players to inject more creativity into 1v1 situations. Take more defined touches, make tighter turns, and explode into attack more dynamically than ever before. Responsive: Creative on ball skills, contextual touches, and a re imagining of the control dribble mechanic give players new options when building up attacks in tight spaces. Change direction with ease and feel your player respond when you escape a defender lunging to tackle. Explosive: Authentic and dynamic speed based animations allow you to explode more rapidly from controlled touches into full tilt sprints. Team Styles and Positioning New Player Positioning: With more freedom in motion, your teammates examine the pitch and react accordingly; darting forward in coordinated runs, or moving into space to provide consistent attacking support. New player positioning gives you a well balanced and spread pitch with more opportunities in time and space to read the play. Team Styles: A deep set of authentic playing styles attributed to several teams put the most recognized tactics on the pitch in FIFA 18 now in AI you will immediately recognize the tiki taka of some of Europe’s best clubs or the high pressing style of teams in the Premier League. Feel a change in defensive and attacking approaches every time you choose a new club or opponent. Dynamic Quick Substitutes: All new context based substitution prompts allow players to easily make changes without pausing the match. Whether it's a missed chance, or necessary response to conceding a goal, you can instantly decide if a change is needed without visiting the menu. Immersive Aospheres Regional Aospheres: Authentic sun positions, cinematic aosphere grading, signature pitch side fixtures, authentic broadcast overlays in La Liga and MLS, on pitch debris, club and stadium specific banners, adaptive commentary, and changes in pitch quality all come together to bring the most immersive football experiences to life in FIFA 18. High Def Dynamic Crowds: All new individual crowd reactions and expanded regional chant support have you feeding off the energy of your supporters. Hear authentic chants build as you mount an attack, incite realistic excitement when you score and even interact with the crowd while celebrating. Dramatic Moments Wonder Goals: New locomotion and finishing animations unlock more fluid striking and heading, combining to increase the potential for more dramatic finishes. Player Personality ensures the heroes of the game stand tall in the biggest moments, finishing more often on the biggest stages. New Crossing Control: All new crossing controls provide the player with a variety of options to put the ball into the box, creating dynamic attacking chances. Whipped to the spot, arching, and back stick crosses increase the variety of delivery to accurately pick out the attacking player. THE JOURNEY: HUNTER RETURNS The World’s Game takes you on a global journey as Alex Hunter returns along with a star studded cast of characters and top football talent, like Ronaldo and other European stars. After a breathtaking first season in the Premier League, Hunter is gaining recognition from top clubs the world over and he is willing to explore any options coming his way. He feels ready to take the next step, his future is bright, and the world is talking about Hunter….but life in football isn’t always fair. Tour the Football World: From a summer break in Brazil, to a pre season tour in Los Angeles, Alex Hunter experiences diverse football landscapes in a truly global journey. Impactful Decisions: Players will be faced with bigger and more difficult choices that will alter the story with long term consequences. Shape The Journey narrative in a personal way by making decisions that dictate Alex Hunter's career and effect relationships with characters both on and off the pitch. Your Alex Hunter: Personalize the look of Alex Hunter by selecting his hair, tattoos, and clothing from a series of options. You can even pick Alex's dominant foot to make sure he suits your playing style. Local Multiplayer: Play The Journey as a team through local multiplayer, and experience on pitch action with friends. New Playable Characters: Now players have the option to experience short, standalone stories with new playable characters that Alex meets throughout The Journey. text: From the brand Previous page Shop Crocs Collections Visit the Store What makes our products unique? We design unparalleled comfort for everywhere you go while innovating for personalization, so you hold the power to make your Crocs uniquely you. What problem are we solving? Comfort at every level, for the body and soul. We want you to stay true to who you are, what you want, and be able to celebrate your uniqueness. Because when you’re comfortable, you can do anything. How did we get our start? We made our debut in 2002 as a boating shoe and became the shoe of choice for those looking for comfort and style. Today, our shoes are also a blank canvas for artists, partners, and customers so we can create something authentic together. title: TICONDEROGA PENCILS, Wood-Cased #2 HB Soft, Pre-Sharpened with Eraser, Yellow, Six 30ct Packs/180 Count Total (X13830)
text: Product Description With a rich heritage, and origins dating back to 1795, the DIXON Ticonderoga company throughout history has made its mark through quality, integrity, respect and perseverance. Today DIXON Ticonderoga continues to make its mark manufacturing and marketing writing instruments, art supplies and tools for self expression. The Ticonderoga is the world's best Pencil. This Item features 30 pre-sharpened pencils with a satin smooth finish to enhance writing comfort. An exclusive graphite core formula gives you extra smooth performance. Pma certified non-toxic and crafted with premium wood from well managed forests, these top quality pencils feature latex-free erasers to provide easy, clean corrections. Great to keep in a locker, in the glove compartment, in your desk drawer - always sharp, always ready to write. title: APC 3000VA Smart UPS with SmartConnect, SMT3000C Sinewave UPS Battery Backup, AVR, 120V, Line Interactive Uninterruptible Power Supply
text: Product Description Protect your servers, switches, routers and networking devices with the Smart-UPS SMT3000C with APC SmartConnect, the first cloud-enabled UPS for distributed IT. The SMT3000C UPS provides backup battery power in the event of a power outage, while safeguarding your equipment from harmful power conditions, spikes and surges. The included cloud monitoring feature (service-free, no fees required) is accessible from any internet connected device, and maximizes the life and performance of your UPS by providing proactive advice and life-cycle recommendations so you can remotely monitor your power infrastructure from anywhere in the world. Automatic green mode ensures you are operating at the highest levels of efficiency, and intelligent battery management provides real-time monitoring and management through temperature-compensated charging that extends the life of the battery. With a 2700-watt power capacity, battery-backup and surge protection on six outlets, with one switchable outlet group, this UPS is ideal for small and medium sized-businesses. Operating Temperature : 32 - 104 °F (0 - 40 °C) Product Description Protect your servers, switches, routers and networking devices with the Smart-UPS SMT3000C with APC SmartConnect, the first cloud-enabled UPS for distributed IT. Operating Temperature : 32 - 104 °F (0 - 40 °C)From the manufacturer Smart-UPS 3000VA with APC SmartConnect Reliable Backup Power and Protection for Your Valuable IT Equipment Protect your servers, switches, routers and networking devices while providing battery backup power with Smart-UPS SMT3000C with APC SmartConnect, the first cloud-enabled UPS for distributed IT. The service-free cloud monitoring feature is accessible from any internet-connected device, and maximizes the life and performance of your UPS by providing proactive advice and life-cycle recommendations so you can remotely monitor your power infrastructure from anywhere. Next Generation of Smart-UPS An Overview of Smart-UPS and the SmartConnect App APC SmartConnect makes Smart-UPS more adaptable and easier to deploy than ever before, enabling you to view the status of your UPS through a secure web portal.Through this intuitive remote management interface, you’ll receive automatic notifications, firmware updates, and advanced support; providing you with added value – and more importantly – added peace of mind. Why use APC SmartConnect? Secure, remote monitoring Connected Smart-UPS support remote monitoring through a secure web portal, so you can always be up to date on the status of your power infrastructure. Proactive lifecycle alerts Maximize the life span of the UPS and protect your investment with proactive alerts for firmware upgrade, device maintenance, and warranty protection. Cloud enabled as standard Smart-UPS models with SmartConnect are cloud-enabled and have a built-in Ethernet port, making it easy and cost effective to monitor your UPS online. Simple to Use Interface Our simple web interface is designed to support both system administrators and non-tech users alike, with clear notifications in plain language. Getting Started is Easy… Smart-UPS SMT3000C Compare APC Smart-UPS 3000VA / 2700W Battery Power 750VA / 500W 5 Hours & 30 Minutes Runtime at 100 watts 50.5 minutes 6 Main Outlets 6 4 Controlled Outlets 0 Yes LCD Display Yes 3000VA / 2700W Battery Power 1000VA / 750W 5 Hours & 30 Minutes Runtime at 100 watts 1 Hour & 40 Minutes 6 Main Outlets 4 4 Controlled Outlets 4 Yes LCD Display Yes 3000VA / 2700W Battery Power 1500VA / 750W 5 Hours & 30 Minutes Runtime at 100 watts 2 Hours & 52 Minutes 6 Main Outlets 4 4 Controlled Outlets 4 Yes LCD Display Yes 3000VA / 2700W Battery Power 2200VA / 2000W 5 Hours & 30 Minutes Runtime at 100 watts 5 Hours & 39 Minutes 6 Main Outlets 6 4 Controlled Outlets 4 Yes LCD Display Yes Previous page Smart-UPS SMT750C Smart-UPS SMT1000C Smart-UPS SMT1500C Smart-UPS SMT2200C Next page Learn More Learn More Learn More Learn More Who are Connected Smart-UPS for? Connected Smart-UPS are for small to medium businesses who do not have the time or resources to monitor their UPS devices but understand the importance of doing so, or who have trusted a Partner with this task. Is APC SmartConnect compatible with RMMs? Yes, APC SmartConnect is compatible and has seamless integration with leading RMM solutions (Kaseya VSA and ConnectWise Automate), so the APC UPS and customer IT can be monitored from a single platform. What if I need a solution for an environment with more than 25 racks? Our vendor-neutral cloud-based software, Ecostruxure IT, monitors critical equipment and delivers insights and smart alarms directly to your smartphone, making it ideal for customers requiring visibility into UPS, cooling, power and more. What do switchable outlet groups allow me to do? Switchable outlet groups provide greater control, allowing you to reboot hung devices, program sequenced on-and-off and non-critical load shedding of equipment. Does this UPS come with PowerChute software? Yes. The UPS includes a CD with PowerChute Business Edition software. This software provides safe shutdown in the event of an extended power outage while preventing data corruption. It also allows you to monitor your equipment’s energy consumption.

This software provides safe shutdown in the event of an extended power outage while preventing data corruption. It also allows you to monitor your equipment’s energy consumption.

title: LIVN LIFE Outdoor Waterproof Picnic Blankets Extra Large. Sandproof & Waterproof Blanket for Beach, Park, Camping, Festivals or Travel. Large Picnic Blanket but Portable and Foldable (Blue/Orange)
text: Product Description LIVN LIFE Picnic Blanket and Beach Blanket. The Day just Gets Better The only thing missing from this photo is being comfortable on a LIVN LIFE Picnic Blanket. The LIVN LIFE Picnic Blanket is designed to keep you protected from damp grass, sand, leaves and dirt so you enjoy your day. Read more Four Vibrant Colors To Choose From Unique Design in Red Tones Who said Picnic Blankets or Beach Blankets should be stripped or checkered? We didn't. We actually looked for something different but made sure the quality was there. Unique Design In OrangeTones Who said that all Picnic Blankets and Beach Blankets should be fluffy and the leaves stick to the blanket like velco or the sand never comes out. We didn't. We looked for a product that was sandproof, water proof and easy to carry. Unique Design In Fuscia Tones Who said that all Picnic Blankets and Beach Blankets should be padded? We didn't. Most people just want something to throw on the grass, the beach, the back yard, at the festival or the game but small enough to keep in the car without the bulk and they remain dry and comfortable when using it. Unique Design In dark Tones Who said that all Beach Blankets should be Blue or Green? We didn't. We wanted to be bold. Since the release we have been overwhelmed by the demand and great reviews and thankful that you want to be different as well. Read more Key Benefits of the LIVN LIFE Picnic Blanket and Beach Blanket Strong and Durable Picnic Blanket and Beach Blanket Our Picnic Blankets/ Beach Blankets are constructed of 2 layers. Top Layer They are bonded together to form a strong bond. Please Review Video To understand the thickness and materials. 600D Oxford Polyester Fabric that is water resistant and resists wear. It is a heavy duty fabric known for its strength and durability & used in products like backpacks and children's camp chairs. It is not plastic . Bottom Layer Waterproof PVC (Plastic) layer to keep you dry. For a closer look check out our Video. Waterproof and Sandproof Picnic and Beach Blanket The PVC backing ensures that you keep dry and leaves, grass and sand don't stick to the surface. If it does get wet you can just wipe dry with a towel when packing up. Easy Clean Fabric The top layer is water resistant so if you get any spills you can just blot up with a cloth. If it is food or mud you can use water or a mid detergent for heavier stains or just get a hose and hose it down and leave to dry. Due to the protective surfaces do not machine wash. Foldable Picnic Blanket and Beach Blanket The LIVN LIFE picnic blanket/Beach Blanket folds up so it can easily be carried or fit nicely in the car, RV or boat for when you need it. We include folding instructions and care instructions but once you have done it a couple of times we are confident that you will have no problems folding in a less than a minute.
