title: French Rolling Pin for Baking 18 Inch - Gifbera Better Wood Beech Dough Roller Baking Utensils for Pizza Bread Pastry Fondant
text: Product Description Professional Bakeware Supplier GIFBERA Better Bakeware - Everything we create begins with the finest materials and the extreme craftsmanship! BAKE WITH QUALITY EVERY DAY We know quality. From our specialty rolling pins to well-used cupcake liners, we give you new reasons to celebrate all of life’s moments—both big and small. It’s about getting more out of today and bringing everyone back to the table. We deliver quality products for quality time. Better Wood Tapered Rolling Pin The choice of countless professional pastry chefs, this tapered beech rolling pin offers outstanding maneuverability and a sensitive feel. The angled ends facilitate shaping the dough, while the flat, slim center lets you roll it to a smooth finish at the desired thickness. Crafted from hand-finished solid New England beech wood. Lightweight, tapered design is easy to maneuver and pivot to create perfect rounds of pastry. Long, slender proportions allow you to flip rolled dough over pin and ease it gently into baking pan. Due to natural color variations inherent in the wood, no two pins are exactly alike. 1 1/2 inch diam., 18'' long overall. Weight: 0.55lb Hand-wash. Dry thoroughly. Occasionally rub pin with food-safe, seed-based oil to protect and condition wood Read more Read more Made of Beech, a hardwood prized for its strength, smoothness, and durability. Lightweight but durable beech construction with smooth surface that’s highly resistant to scratching and splintering. No paint and wax. The angle of the LED light panels are adjusted to illuminate different area Ranges. 4. Busypiggy fan not only can cool you down but also can be used as emergency power to charge your phone, GPS, MP3, or iPod, etc. 5. Top with solar panel, Place the solar charging panel to the sun to charge the fan in an emergency situation. 6. Foldable hook, convenient use for tent, fishing, camping, study, work, etc. 7. Made of high-quality ABS material, it is strong and resistant to falling. This futon cover set features a classic double-corded design and is available in eighteen striking color options.From the manufacturer Our Story Blazing Needles, L.P. began as an affiliate company to International Caravan, Inc. Its first manufactured products were papasan cushions for papasans imported by International Caravan in the late 1970s. As time progressed, Blazing Needles began to manufacture more and more items for International Caravan’s furniture collection, adding a much needed bit of customizability and comfort to a wide variety of products. In the early 1990s, Blazing Needles began to manufacture a wide variety of futons, and over time established itself as one of the more prolific futon mattress manufacturers in the United States. It was also around this time that Blazing Needles began to do larger, bulk contract orders for wholesale customers and third-party cut-and-sew projects alike. Read more

Read more Airflow adjustable If you blow the dog head and dog belly, you can not use so large airflow . So you have two airflow options. You can easily adjust the size of the airflow. Quality switch & stable motors They are specially used for 110V circuits and all through rigorous system test. Can run uninterrupted for more than 24 hours New method of Noise Reduction Four levels noise reduction device at the air inlets . The sound is not overpowering. title: Helen's Asian Kitchen 97139 Silicone Wok Tool, 14"
text: Product Description Highlights: Size: 14" Updated design on a traditional classic wok tool Safe for use on nonstick cookware wont scratch or remove seasoned surfaces from steel woks Heat resistant to 550F Dishwasher safe Product Description Highlights: Size: 14" Updated design on a traditional classic wok tool Safe for use on nonstick cookware wont scratch or remove seasoned surfaces from steel woks Heat resistant to 550F Dishwasher safeFrom the brand HELEN’S ASIAN KITCHEN Helen Chen is a leading Asian culinary expert, cooking instructor, and developer of Helen's Asian Kitchen cookware and cooking tools. Previous page HELEN’S ASIAN KITCHEN Dedicated to the art of Eastern cooking CUSTOMER FAVORITES “I learned to cook the old fashioned way—from my mother—with a style that emphasizes the delights and comforts of home-style dishes. I love to teach the methods of Chinese cooking and created my Helen’s Asian Kitchen line to make the process even more enjoyable to the home chef.” - Helen Chen Helen's Asian Kitchen is a member of HIC – Harold Import Co.'s exclusive family of brands. HIC – Harold Import Co. is a USA-based, family-owned business. How did we get our start? Helen learned to cook from her mother. She combines the comfort of home-style dishes with heart-healthy oils and readily available market ingredients—making cooking great Asian food easier for everyone. What products do we offer? We offer a full range of woks, bamboo steamers, spider strainers, sushi tools, chopsticks, bamboo spatulas, and many other cooking accessories. What makes our products special? Helen Chen's unique line of Asian cooking & kitchen tools were developed through many years of culinary experience and provides high-quality standards. Next page
